## <a name="authentication-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-159">Autentifikavimo įvykiai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-159">Authentication events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-160">Šie diagnostikos duomenų įvykiai renkami, kai „Office“ bando gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą (tyliai arba pateikdamas raginimus).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-160">These diagnostic data events are collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroidmsaguesttoaad"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-161">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-161">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-162">Šis įvykis padeda suprasti, kiek vartotojų gauna raginimus įvesti asmeninės paskyros slaptažodį bandant pasiekti darbo paskyros šaltinį, kadangi jų asmeninė paskyra gali būti galiojantis svečias jų darbo paskyros nuomininkui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-162">This event helps in understanding how many users are getting prompted for providing personal account password, while accessing work resource, as their personal account could be a valid guest to work account's tenant.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-163">Šie duomenys padeda suprasti, kiek vartotojų gauna pakartotinius raginimus prisijungti, ir nustatyti prioritetus AAD atpažinimo ženklo įsigijimui, kuris pagal nutylėjimą yra „Microsoft“ paskyros SAML pasireiškime.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-163">This data helps us understand how many users are going through the pain of sign in re-prompts to prioritize AAD token acquisition silently based on a Microsoft account SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) assertion.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-164">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-164">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-165">**Žymė** - Nurodo, kad vartotojas gavo raginimą prisijungti prie asmeninės paskyros, kai bandė pasiekti darbo paskyros šaltinį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-165">**Tag** - Indicates that user got sign-in prompt for personal account, while accessing work account resource.</span></span>


### <a name="officeidentityfbapromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-166">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-166">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-167">Renkama, kai „Office“ rodo vartotojui formomis pagrįsto autentifikavimo prisijungimo raginimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-167">Collected when Office shows the user a Forms-Based-Auth sign-in prompt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-168">Kartu su tyliu atpažinimo ženklų gavimu, naudojami autentifikavimo raginimai siekiant nustatyti, ar vartotojo autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama. Tai vartotojui iš esmės reiškia, kad kliento būsena bus Neprisijungęs, arba, blogiausiu atveju, dėl netinkamo autentifikavimo gali būti negauta licencija ir bus visiškai negalima naudoti kliento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-168">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts are used to determine if user is in a broken authentication state which, for the user, results in what is essentially an Offline Client state, or in the worst case, broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-169">Formomis pagrįsto autentifikavimo (FBA) prisijungimo raginimai naudojami kai kuriais vietinio autentifikavimo scenarijais ir paprastai norime įsitikinti, kad tai nevyksta, nes visi turėtų naudoti šiuolaikinį autentifikavimą dėl su FBA siejamų saugos pažeidžiamumų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-169">Forms-Based-Auth (FBA) sign-in prompts are used for some on-premises authentication scenarios and typically we want to make sure this isn't happening, as everyone should be using Modern-Auth because of security vulnerabilities associated with FBA.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-170">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-170">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-171">**AuthScheme** – naudojama autentifikavimo schema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-171">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-172">**DocumentUrlHash** – prašomas užšifruotas URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-172">**DocumentUrlHash** - an encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-173">**EndTag** – FBA formos pabaigos žymė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-173">**EndTag** - the tag where FBA form is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-174">**Flags** – nebenaudojama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-174">**Flags** - Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-175">**FlowTag** – FBA formos pradžios žymė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-175">**FlowTag** - the tag where FBA form is started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-176">**LastError** – pateiktas klaidos kodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-176">**LastError** – the error code returned</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-177">**PromptEndTime** – raginimo pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-177">**PromptEndTime** - the time when then prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-178">**PromptStartTime** – raginimo pradžios laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-178">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-179">**Result** – ar autentifikavimas sėkmingas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-179">**Result** - whether the authentication succeeded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-180">**SessionEndTime** – įvykio seanso pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-180">**SessionEndTime** – the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-181">**Timeout** – raginimo skirtojo laiko pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-181">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt timed out</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysignoutevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-182">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-182">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-183">Renkama, kai vartotojas atsijungia nuo „Office“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-183">Collected when a user signs out of Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-184">Žinant, kad vartotojas atsijungė, galima klasifikuoti kitus įvykius, pvz., raginimus, kaip numatyta, kad šie įvykiai būtų tinkamai apskaičiuoti patikimumo / parengimo pateikti metrikoje ir būtų išvengta įspėjimų arba komponavimo versijų keitimų atšaukimo darant klaidingą prielaidą, kad vartotojui pateikiami netikėti prisijungimo raginimai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-184">Knowing the user is signed out makes it possible to classify other events, such as prompts, as expected, so those events can be correctly computed in reliability / ship-readiness metrics and avoid alerting or rolling back builds on the faulty premise that the user is experiencing unexpected sign-in prompts.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-185">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-185">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-186">**FlowEndTime** – atsijungimo veiksmo pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-186">**FlowEndTime** - the time when the sign out action ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-187">**FlowStartTime** – atsijungimo veiksmo pradžios laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-187">**FlowStartTime** - the time when the sign out action started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-188">**IdentityErrorState** – bet kokia tapatybės klaidos būsena atsijungiant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-188">**IdentityErrorState** - any identity error state during sign out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-189">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** – užšifruotas tapatybės ID, kurio atsijungimo procesas vykdomas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-189">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** - the encrypted identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-190">**IdentityProviderType** – tapatybės, kurios atsijungimo procesas vykdomas, tapatybės teikėjas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-190">**IdentityProviderType** - the identity provider of the identity being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-191">**IdentityUniqueID** – tapatybės ID, kurio atsijungimo procesas vykdomas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-191">**IdentityUniqueID** - the identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-192">**SessionEndTime** – įvykio seanso pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-192">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-193">**SignOutUserAction** – nurodo, kad vartotojas inicijuoja atsijungimo veiksmą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-193">**SignOutUserAction** - Indicates the user initiates the sign out action</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysspipromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-194">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-194">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-195">Renkama, kai „Office“ rodo vartotojui „Windows“ SSPI prisijungimo raginimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-195">Collected when Office shows the user a Windows SSPI sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-196">Kartu su tyliu atpažinimo ženklų gavimu, autentifikavimo raginimai lemia, ar vartotojo autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama (dėl jos kliento būsena tampa Neprisijungęs).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-196">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-197">Dėl netinkamo autentifikavimo gali būti negauta licencija ir gali visiškai nepavykti naudoti kliento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-197">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-198">„Windows“ SSPI raginimai naudojami autentifikuojant per „Exchange“ (el. paštui sinchronizuoti), kai vartotojo „Exchange“ išteklius nebuvo nustatytas naudoti kelių dalių autentifikavimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-198">Windows SSPI prompts are used for authenticating with Exchange (for mail synchronizing) when the user's Exchange resource hasn't been set up for multi-factor authentication.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-199">Šie įvykiai, kartu su „Office.MATS“ vardų srities įvykiais, naudojami šiais tikslais:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-199">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-200">1\) Siekiant nustatyti, ar klientai gali sėkmingai gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą, ar jų autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-200">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-201">2\) Siekiant įvertinti, ar kliente arba paslaugose padaryti keitimai lėmė kritinį vartotojo autentifikavimo patirties ir patikimumo suprastėjimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-201">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-202">3\) Kai įvyksta triktis, šie signalai perduoda svarbius trikties kodus iš atsakingo komponento („Office“ kliento kodo, autentifikavimo bibliotekų arba tarnybų), kuriuos galima naudoti nustatant, diagnozuojant ir mažinant poveikį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-202">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-203">4\) Šie signalai siunčiami į įvairias parengimo pateikti ir sveikatos stebėjimo programas, kurios suaktyvina įspėjimus, kad mūsų inžinieriai galėtų greitai imtis problemos sprendimo ir būtų greičiau sumažintas kritinių vartotojams dirbti neleidžiančių trikčių poveikis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-203">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors, which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-204">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-204">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-205">**AllowSavedCreds** – ar nauji kredencialai išlaikomi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-205">**AllowSavedCreds** - whether the new credential is persisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-206">**AuthScheme** – naudojama autentifikavimo schema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-206">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-207">**CredsSaved** – ar nauji kredencialai įrašomi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-207">**CredsSaved** - whether the new credential is saved</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-208">**DocumentUrlHash** – prašomas užšifruotas URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-208">**DocumentUrlHash** - the encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-209">**EndTag** – raginimo pabaigos žymė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-209">**EndTag** - the tag where the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-210">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – ar nauja tapatybė yra galiojanti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-210">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – whether the new identity is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-211">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** – užšifruotas naujas tapatybės ID užbaigus raginimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-211">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** - the encrypted new identity ID after prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-212">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** – naujas tapatybės teikėjas užbaigus raginimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-212">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-213">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** – naujas tapatybės ID užbaigus raginimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-213">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-214">**OutStatus** – ar raginimo išvestis yra galiojanti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-214">**OutStatus** - whether the prompt output is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-215">**PromptEndTime** - raginimo pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-215">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-216">**PromptFailedTag** – žymė, nurodanti SSPI raginimo triktį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-216">**PromptFailedTag** - the tag that indicates SSPI prompt failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-217">**PromptFlow** – žymė, kuri iškvietė SSPI raginimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-217">**PromptFlow** - the tag that invoked the SSPI prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-218">**PromptStartTime** – raginimo pradžios laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-218">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-219">**Proxy** – ar naudojamas tarpinis serveris</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-219">**Proxy** - if proxy is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-220">**ServerHash** – užšifruotas serverio adresas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-220">**ServerHash** - the encrypted server address</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-221">**SessionEndTime** – įvykio seanso pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-221">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-222">**Timeout** – raginimo skirtojo laiko pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-222">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-223">**UiMessage** – vartotojo sąsajos pranešimas raginime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-223">**UiMessage** - the UI message in the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-224">**UserNameHash** – užšifruotas vartotojo vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-224">**UserNameHash** - the encrypted user name</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitywin32prompt"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-225">Office.Identity.Win32Prompt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-225">Office.Identity.Win32Prompt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-226">Renkama, kai „Office“ rodo vartotojui kelių dalių autentifikavimo prisijungimo raginimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-226">Collected when Office shows the user a multi-factor authentication sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-227">Kartu su tyliu atpažinimo ženklų gavimu, autentifikavimo raginimai lemia, ar vartotojo autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama (dėl jos kliento būsena tampa Neprisijungęs).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-227">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-228">Dėl netinkamo autentifikavimo gali būti negauta licencija ir gali visiškai nepavykti naudoti kliento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-228">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-229">Šie įvykiai, kartu su „Office.MATS“ vardų srities įvykiais, naudojami šiais tikslais:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-229">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-230">1\) Siekiant nustatyti, ar klientai gali sėkmingai gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą, ar jų autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-230">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered in to a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-231">2\) Siekiant įvertinti, ar kliente arba paslaugose padaryti keitimai lėmė kritinį vartotojo autentifikavimo patirties ir patikimumo suprastėjimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-231">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-232">3\) Kai įvyksta triktis, šie signalai perduoda svarbius trikties kodus iš atsakingo komponento („Office“ kliento kodo, autentifikavimo bibliotekų arba tarnybų), kuriuos galima naudoti nustatant, diagnozuojant ir mažinant poveikį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-232">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-233">4\) Šie signalai siunčiami į įvairias parengimo pateikti ir sveikatos stebėjimo programas, kurios suaktyvina įspėjimus, kad mūsų inžinieriai galėtų greitai imtis problemos sprendimo ir būtų greičiau sumažintas kritinių vartotojams dirbti neleidžiančių trikčių poveikis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-233">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors, which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-234">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-234">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-235">**AdalWAMUsed** – žymė, kuri nurodo rezultatą, jei naudojamas ADAL-atop-WAM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-235">**AdalWAMUsed** – the tag that indicates result if ADAL-atop-WAM is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-236">**CallTag** – žymė, kuri nurodo, kas iškviečia prisijungimo vartotojo sąsają</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-236">**CallTag** – the tag that indicates the caller of sign in UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-237">**Context** – raginimo prisijungimo kontekstas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-237">**Context** - the sign in context for the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-238">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** – žymė, kur prašomas tapatybės teikėjas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-238">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** - the tag where the identity provider is requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-239">**HrdShownTag** – žymė, kur rodomas HRD prisijungimo dialogo langas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-239">**HrdShownTag** - the tag where the HRD sign in dialog is shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-240">**IdentityProviderResulted** – prašomas tapatybės teikėjo tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-240">**IdentityProviderResulted** - the identity provider type it is requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-241">**IdPFlowTag** – žymė, kuri nurodo tapatybės užklausos rezultatą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-241">**IdPFlowTag** - the tag that indicates the identity request result</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-242">**LastLoginDelta** – laiko pokytis nuo paskutinio sėkmingo prisijungimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-242">**LastLoginDelta** - the time delta from last successful login</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-243">**NewIdentity\_ErrorState** – ar tapatybė galioja po raginimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-243">**NewIdentity\_ErrorState** - whether the identity is valid after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-244">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** – naujas tapatybės teikėjo tipas po raginimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-244">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider type after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-245">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** – naujas tapatybės ID, pateiktas po raginimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-245">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID returned after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-246">**PromptCorrelation** – raginimo sąsajos ID diagnostikos tikslais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-246">**PromptCorrelation** - the prompt correlation ID for diagnostic purpose</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-247">**PromptEndTime** - raginimo pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-247">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-248">**PromptStartTime** – raginimo pradžios laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-248">**PromptStartTime** – the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-249">**SessionEndTime** – įvykio seanso pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-249">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-250">**ShowUIResult** – rezultato kodas, pateiktas iš raginimo vartotojo sąsajos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-250">**ShowUIResult** – the result code returned from the prompt UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-251">**StartTag** – žymė, kur pradėtas „Win32“ raginimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-251">**StartTag** – the tag where Win32 prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-252">**Timeout** – raginimo skirtojo laiko pabaigos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-252">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-253">**WasIdentitySignedOut** – ar vartotojas atsijungęs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-253">**WasIdentitySignedOut** - whether the user is signed out</span></span>

### <a name="officematsactionofficewin32-officematsactionofficewinrt"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-254">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-254">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-255">Tolesnis aprašas taikomas ir „Win32“, ir „WinRT“ įvykiams (pavadinimas priklauso nuo platformos)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-255">The following description applies for both Win32 and WinRT events (the name depends on platform.)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-256">„Microsoft“ autentifikavimo telemetrijos sistemos (MATS) įvykiai renkami, kai „Office“ bando gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą (tyliai arba pateikdamas raginimus).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-256">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-257">Kai bandymas gauti nepavyksta, įtraukiama klaidos informacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-257">When acquisition attempts fail, error information is included.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-258">Šie įvykiai padeda vartotojams išvengti netinkamos autentifikavimo būsenos:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-258">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-259">1\) Nustatant, ar klientai gali sėkmingai gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą, ar jų autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-259">1\) Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-260">2\) Įvertinant, ar kliente arba paslaugose padaryti keitimai lėmė kritinį vartotojo autentifikavimo patirties ir patikimumo suprastėjimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-260">2\) Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-261">3\) Kai įvyksta triktis, šie signalai perduoda svarbius trikties kodus iš atsakingo komponento („Office“ kliento kodo, autentifikavimo bibliotekų arba tarnybų), kuriuos galima naudoti nustatant, diagnozuojant ir mažinant poveikį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-261">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-262">4\) Šie signalai siunčiami į įvairias parengimo pateikti ir sveikatos stebėjimo programas, kurios suaktyvina įspėjimus, kad mūsų inžinieriai galėtų greitai imtis problemos sprendimo ir būtų greičiau sumažintas kritinių trikčių poveikis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-262">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors, which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-263">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-263">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-264">**Actiontype** – kuri autentifikavimo biblioteka naudojama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-264">**Actiontype** - Which authentication library is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-265">**Appaudience** – ar programa sukurta vidiniam, ar išoriniam naudojimui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-265">**Appaudience** - Is the app build for internal or external use</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-266">**Appforcedprompt** – ar programa perrašė talpyklą ir priverstinai parodė raginimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-266">**Appforcedprompt** - Did the app override cache and force a prompt to be shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-267">**Appname** – programos, kurią naudojant autentifikuojama, pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-267">**Appname** - Name of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-268">**Appver** – programos, kurią naudojant identifikuojama, versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-268">**Appver** - Version of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-269">**Askedforcreds** – ar programa paprašė vartotojo įvesti kredencialus atliekant šį veiksmą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-269">**Askedforcreds** - Did the application ask the user to enter credentials for this action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-270">**Authoutcome** – ar autentifikavimo bandymas pavyko, nepavyko, ar buvo atšauktas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-270">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-271">**Blockingprompt** – ar programa pateikė raginimą, reikalaujantį vartotojo sąveikos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-271">**Blockingprompt** - Did the application throw a prompt requiring user interaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-272">**Correlationid** – GUID, naudojamas siejant su paslaugų duomenimis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-272">**Correlationid** - GUID used for joining with services data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-273">**Count** – įvykių skaičius agregavimo atvejais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-273">**Count** - Count of events in cases of aggregation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-274">**Data\_accounttype** – vartotojo ar organizacijos paskyra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-274">**Data\_accounttype** - Consumer or organizational account</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-275">**Devicenetworkstate** – ar vartotojas buvo prisijungęs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-275">**Devicenetworkstate** - Was the user online</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-276">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** – anoniminis įrenginio ID, naudojamas vertinant įrenginio patirtį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-276">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Anonymous device ID used to measure device experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-277">**Duration** – kiek laiko truko autentifikavimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-277">**Duration** - How long the authentication took</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-278">**Duration_Max** – jei šis signalas sujungiamas, ilgiausia bet kurio suvestinio įvykio trukmė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-278">**Duration_Max** - If this signal is aggregated, the maximum duration of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-279">**Duration_Min** – jei šis signalas sujungiamas, trumpiausia bet kurio suvestinio įvykio trukmė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-279">**Duration_Min** - If this signal is aggregated, the minimum duration of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-280">**Duration_Sum** – jei šis signalas sujungiamas, visų sudėtų įvykių trukmės suma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-280">**Duration_Sum** - If this signal is aggregated, the sum of the durations of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-281">**Endtime** – kada baigtas autentifikavimo įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-281">**Endtime** - When the authentication event ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-282">**Error** – klaidos kodas, jei autentifikavimas nepavyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-282">**Error** - Error code if the authentication failed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-283">**Errordescription** – trumpas klaidos aprašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-283">**Errordescription** - Brief description of the error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-284">**Errorsource** – ar klaida įvyko iš paslaugos, autentifikavimo bibliotekos, ar programos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-284">**Errorsource** - Did the error come from service, authentication library, or application</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-285">**Identityservice** – ar buvo iškviesta „Microsoft“ tarnybos paskyra (MSA), ar „Azure Active Directory“ (AAD) paslauga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-285">**Identityservice** - Was Microsoft Service Account (MSA) or Azure Active Directory (AAD) service invoked</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-286">**Interactiveauthcontainer** – kokio tipo raginimas buvo parodytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-286">**Interactiveauthcontainer** - What type of prompt was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-287">**Issilent** – ar raginimas buvo parodytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-287">**Issilent** - Was a prompt shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-288">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** – „Azure Active Directory“ autentifikavimo bibliotekos (ADAL) versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-288">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** - Version of the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-289">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** – šio autentifikavimo bandymo klaidos kodas, perduotas autentifikavimo bibliotekos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-289">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** - Error code emitted by authentication library for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-290">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** – iškviesta šio autentifikavimo bandymo API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-290">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** - API invoked for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-291">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** – „Azure Active Directory“ tarnybos, atsakingos už vartojo autentifikavimą, URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-291">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** – Azure Active Directory authority URL responsible for authenticating the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-292">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** – vartotojo / „Microsoft“ paslaugų teikimo sutartis (MSA) ar organizacijos / „Azure Active Directory“ (AAD); šiuo metu visada AAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-292">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** – Consumer / Microsoft Service Agreement (MSA) vs organizational / Azure Active Directory (AAD); currently always AAD</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** – pasako, ar autentifikavimas baigtas paslaugos pusėje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** – Tells whether authentication completed on the service-side</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** – pasako, ar ADAL naudojo autentifikavimo tvarkytuvę</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** - Tells whether ADAL used a broker for authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** – pasako tvarkytuvės pavadinimą (pvz., „Windows“ paskyros tvarkytuvė)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** – Tells the name of the broker (for example, Windows Account Management)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** – pasako tvarkytuvės versiją (jei naudota)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** - Tells the version of the broker if used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** – ADAL įvykdytų talpyklos įvykių skaičius gaunant atpažinimo ženklą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** - Number of cache events ADAL performed while retrieving token</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** – jei šis signalas yra agreguotas, didžiausias vieno iš agreguotų įvykių talpyklos įvykių skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-299">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** – jei šis signalas yra agreguotas, mažiausias vieno iš agreguotų įvykių talpyklos įvykių skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-299">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** – jei šis signalas yra agreguotas, visų agreguotų įvykių talpyklos įvykių suma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the cache events of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-301">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** – kiek kartų API skaitė iš disko talpyklos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-301">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** - How many times the API read from the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-302">Pateikiamas, jei skaityta bent vieną kartą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-302">Present if there was at least one read.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-303">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** – kiek kartų nepavyko skaitymo iš disko talpyklos procesas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-303">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache read failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-304">Pateikiamas, jei buvo bent viena klaida.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-304">Is present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-305">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** – ADAL klaidos kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-305">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-306">Pateikiamas, jei buvo bent viena skaitymo klaida.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-306">Present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-307">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** – sistemos klaidos kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-307">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-308">Pateikiamas, jei buvo bent viena skaitymo klaida.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-308">Is present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-309">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_count** – kiek kartų API rašė į disko talpyklą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-309">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_count** - How many times the API wrote to the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-310">Pateikiamas, jei rašyta bent vieną kartą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-310">Present if there was at least one write.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-311">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** – kiek kartų nepavyko rašymo į disko talpyklą procesas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-311">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache-write failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-312">Pateikiamas, jei buvo bent viena klaida.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-312">Present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-313">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** – ADAL klaidos kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-313">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-314">Pateikiamas, jei buvo bent viena rašymo klaida.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-314">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-315">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** – sistemos klaidos kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-315">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-316">Pateikiamas, jei buvo bent viena rašymo klaida.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-316">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-317">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** – AAD programos ID, kuriam pritaikyta maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-317">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** - Hashed AAD app ID</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-318">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** – ar atpažinimo ženklo egzistavimo laikotarpis pailgintas (teisinga arba klaidinga).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-318">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** - True/false telling if the token has an extended lifetime.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-319">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_coun** t – ADAL atliktų HTTP iškvietimų skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-319">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_coun** t - Count of HTTP calls made by ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-320">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_max** – jei šis signalas yra agreguotas, bet kurio agreguoto įvykio maksimalus ADAL atliktų HTTP iškvietimų skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-320">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-321">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** – jei šis signalas yra agreguotas, bet kurio agreguoto įvykio minimalus ADAL atliktų HTTP iškvietimų skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-321">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-322">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_sum** – jei šis signalas yra agreguotas, visų agreguotų įvykių ADAL atliktų HTTP iškvietimų suma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-322">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the HTTP calls made by ADAL of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-323">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_silent\_ui** – ar ADAL parodė vartotojo sąsają (raginimą) (teisinga arba klaidinga).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-323">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_silent\_ui** - True/false telling if UI was shown (prompt) by ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_successful** – ar ADAL API pavyko (teisinga arba klaidinga).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_successful** - True/false telling if ADAL API succeeded.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_logging\_pii\_enabled** - ar įgalintas visas ADAL registravimo žurnale režimas (teisinga arba klaidinga).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_logging\_pii\_enabled** - True/false telling if ADAL full logging mode is enabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-326">Šie duomenys registruojami tik vietoje; jie neperduodami telemetrijoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-326">This data is only logged locally, not emitted in telemetry.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-327">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_oauth\_error\_code** – „OAuth“ protokolo klaidos kodas, kurį pateikė paslauga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-327">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_oauth\_error\_code** – OAuth protocol error code returned by the service.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-328">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_prompt\_behavior** – HTTP parametras (Prisijungimas / Nėra), perduotas į paslaugą, siekiant nurodyti, ar galima parodyti vartotojo sąsają.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-328">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_prompt\_behavior** - log-in or none HTTP parameter passed to service to specify if user interface can be shown.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-329">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_request\_id** – ADAL į paslaugą perduotos užklausos operacinis GUID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-329">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_request\_id** - Transactional GUID for the request emitted by ADAL to the service.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-330">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_code** – HTTP atsakymo kodas iš paslaugos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-330">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_code** - HTTP response code from the service.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-331">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_time** – per kiek laiko paslauga atsakė ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-331">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_response\_time** - How long it took service to return to ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-352">**Promptreasoncorrelationid** – raginimai, tai yra kito įvykio koreliacijos ID, kuriame paaiškinama, kodėl vartotojas gali matyti autentifikavimo raginimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-352">**Promptreasoncorrelationid** – For prompts, this is the correlation id of another event which explains why the user might be seeing an authentication prompt.</span></span>

### <a name="officematsoneauthactionmicrosoftofficewin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-366">Office.MATS.OneAuth.ActionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-366">Office.MATS.OneAuth.ActionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-367">„Microsoft“ autentifikavimo telemetrijos sistemos (MATS) įvykiai renkami, kai „Office“ bando gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą (tyliai arba pateikdamas raginimus).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-367">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-368">Kai bandymas gauti nepavyksta, įtraukiama klaidos informacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-368">When acquisition attempts fail, error information is included.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-369">Šie įvykiai padeda vartotojams išvengti netinkamos autentifikavimo būsenos:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-369">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

1) <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-370">Nustatant, ar klientai gali sėkmingai gauti paslaugos autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą, ar jų autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-370">Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token from the service, or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

2) <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-371">Įvertinant, ar kliente arba paslaugose padaryti keitimai lėmė kritinį vartotojo autentifikavimo patirties ir patikimumo suprastėjimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-371">Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

3) <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-372">Kai įvyksta triktis, šie signalai perduoda svarbius trikties kodus iš atsakingo komponento („Office“ kliento kodo, autentifikavimo bibliotekų arba tarnybų), kuriuos galima naudoti nustatant, diagnozuojant ir mažinant poveikį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-372">When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

4) <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-373">Šie signalai siunčiami į įvairias parengimo pateikti ir sveikatos stebėjimo programas, kurios suaktyvina įspėjimus, kad mūsų inžinieriai galėtų greitai imtis problemos sprendimo ir būtų greičiau sumažinta kritinių trikčių rizika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-373">These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors, which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-374">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-374">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-375">**Accounttype** – paskyros, naudojamos šiame autentifikavimo įvykiui, tipas, pvz., vartotojo arba organizacijos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-375">**Accounttype** - Type of the account used for this authentication event, for example, consumer or organizational.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-376">**Actionname** – aiškus šio įvykio pavadinimas, jei jis buvo pateiktas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-376">**Actionname** - Friendly name for this event, if one was provided.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-377">**Actiontype** – nurodo naudojamos autentifikavimo bibliotekos tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-377">**Actiontype** - Specifies the type of authentication library in use.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-378">**Appaudience** – ar programa sukurta vidiniam, ar išoriniam naudojimui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-378">**Appaudience** - Is the app build for internal or external use</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-379">**Appforcedprompt** – ar programa perrašė talpyklą ir priverstinai parodė raginimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-379">**Appforcedprompt** - Did the app override cache and force a prompt to be shown</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-380">**Appname** – programos, kurią naudojant autentifikuojama, pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-380">**Appname** - Name of the application doing authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-381">**Appver** – programos, kurią naudojant identifikuojama, versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-381">**Appver** - Version of the application doing authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-382">**Askedforcreds** – ar programa paprašė vartotojo įvesti kredencialus atliekant šį veiksmą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-382">**Askedforcreds** - Did the application ask the user to enter credentials for this action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-383">**Authoutcome** – ar autentifikavimo bandymas pavyko, nepavyko, ar buvo atšauktas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-383">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-384">**Blockingprompt** – ar programa pateikė raginimą, reikalaujantį vartotojo sąveikos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-384">**Blockingprompt** -  Did the application throw a prompt requiring user interaction</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-385">**Correlationid** – identifikatorius, naudojamas prijungti informaciją apie šį atskirą įvykį prie tarnybų duomenų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-385">**Correlationid** - Identifier used to join information regarding this individual event with services data</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-386">**Count** – bendras agreguotų veiksmų, pateiktų šiame viename duomenų įvykyje, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-386">**Count** - The total number of aggregated actions reported in this one data event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-387">**Devicenetworkstate** – įrenginys, prijungtas prie interneto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-387">**Devicenetworkstate** - Is the device connected to the internet.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-388">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** – anoniminis įrenginio ID, naudojamas įrenginio autentifikavimo patirties ir patikimumo matavimui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-388">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Anonymous device ID used to measure device-wide authentication experience and reliability.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-389">**Duration** – kiek laiko truko autentifikavimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-389">**Duration** - How long the authentication took</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-390">**duration_max** – maksimali bet kurio iš agreguotų įvykių trukmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-390">**duration_max** - Max duration of any one of the aggregated events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-391">**duration_min** – minimali bet kurio iš agreguotų įvykių trukmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-391">**duration_min** - Min duration of any one of the aggregated events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-392">**duration_sum** – visų agreguotų įvykių trukmės suma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-392">**duration_sum** - Sum of the duration of all the aggregated events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-393">**endtime** – kada baigtas autentifikavimo įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-393">**endtime** - When the authentication event ended</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-394">**error** – klaidos kodas, jei autentifikavimas nepavyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-394">**error** - Error code if the authentication failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-395">**errordescription** – trumpas klaidos aprašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-395">**errordescription** - Brief description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-396">**errorsource** – ar klaida įvyko iš paslaugos, autentifikavimo bibliotekos, ar programos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-396">**errorsource** - Did the error come from service, authentication library, or application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-397">**eventtype** – ar šis įvykis praneša apie autentifikavimo duomenų elementą arba duomenų kokybės klaidos įvykį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-397">**eventtype** - Is this event reporting an authentication datapoint, or a data quality error event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-398">Naudojamas duomenų kokybei matuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-398">Used to measure data quality.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-399">**from_cache** – Bulio logikos, nurodančios, ar įrašas yra iš WAM pagrindinio podėlio, ar priedo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-399">**from_cache** - Boolean representing whether the record is from the WAM core cache, or the plugin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-400">**hasadaltelemetry** – nurodo, ar „Azure Active Directory“ autentifikavimo biblioteka (ADAL) pateikė telemetriją šiam įvykiui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-400">**hasadaltelemetry** - Indicates whether the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL) provided telemetry for this event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-401">**Identityservice** – ar buvo iškviesta „Microsoft“ tarnybos paskyra (MSA), ar „Azure Active Directory“ (AAD) paslauga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-401">**Identityservice** - Was Microsoft Service Account (MSA) or Azure Active Directory (AAD) service invoked</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-402">**Interactiveauthcontainer** – kokio tipo raginimas buvo parodytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-402">**Interactiveauthcontainer** - What type of prompt was shown</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-403">**Issilent** – ar buvo rodomas raginimas arba ar tai buvo tylus (fono) autentifikavimo įvykis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-403">**Issilent** - Was a prompt shown or was this a silent (background) authentication event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-404">**Microsoft_ADAL_adal_version** – „Azure Active Directory“ autentifikavimo bibliotekos (ADAL) versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-404">**Microsoft_ADAL_adal_version** - Version of the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-405">**Microsoft_ADAL_api_error_code** – šio autentifikavimo bandymo klaidos kodas, perduotas autentifikavimo bibliotekos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-405">**Microsoft_ADAL_api_error_code** - Error code emitted by authentication library for this authentication attempt</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-406">**Microsoft_ADAL_api_id** – iškviesta šio autentifikavimo bandymo API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-406">**Microsoft_ADAL_api_id** - API invoked for this authentication attempt</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-407">**Microsoft_ADAL_application_name** – taikomosios programos / proceso, naudojančio ADAL, pavadinimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-407">**Microsoft_ADAL_application_name** - The name of the application / process using ADAL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-557">**WAM_oauth_error_code** – pateikiamas klaidos kodas, kurį pateikė tarnyba, kaip „OAuth“ protokolo dalį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-557">**WAM_oauth_error_code** - Contains the error code returned by the service as part of the oauth protocol.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-558">**WAM_prompt_behavior** – nurodo, ar šį raginimą pateikė programa, arba, ar ši užklausa gali praleisti raginimą, jei ji gali būti autentifikuota tyliai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-558">**WAM_prompt_behavior** - Specifies if this prompt is forced by the app, or, if this request might skip prompting if it can silently authenticate.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-562">**WAM_server_error_code** – tarnybos į WAM pateiktas klaidos kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-562">**WAM_server_error_code** - The error code returned by the service to WAM.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-563">**WAM_server_sub_code** – papildomas klaidos kodas, naudojamas siekiant toliau išskaidyti tarnybos pateiktas gedimo priežastis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-563">**WAM_server_sub_code** - An additional error code used to further break down the causes for failure, returned by the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-565">**WAM_silent_mats** – nenaudojamas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-565">**WAM_silent_mats** - Unused.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-566">**WAM_silent_message** – klaidos pranešimas, susietas su WAM vidiniu automatiniu bandymu prieš pateikiant raginimą vartotojui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-566">**WAM_silent_message** - The error message associated with the internal silent attempt WAM makes, prior to prompting the user.</span></span>

### <a name="officematsoneauthtransactionmicrosoftofficewin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-571">Office.MATS.OneAuth.TransactionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-571">Office.MATS.OneAuth.TransactionMicrosoftOfficeWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-572">„Microsoft“ autentifikavimo telemetrijos sistemos (MATS) įvykiai renkami, kai „Office“ bando gauti autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą (tyliai arba pateikdamas raginimus).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-572">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-573">Šis įvykis yra vieno ar kelių ActionMicrosoftOffice pirminis įvykis, suteikiantis galimybę kartu sugrupuoti susijusius įvykius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-573">This event is a parent of one or more ActionMicrosoftOffice events, allowing related events to be grouped together.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-574">Šie įvykiai padeda vartotojams išvengti netinkamos autentifikavimo būsenos:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-574">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

1) <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-575">Nustatant, ar klientai gali sėkmingai gauti paslaugos autentifikavimo atpažinimo ženklą, ar jų autentifikavimo būsena yra netinkama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-575">Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token from the service, or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

2) <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-576">Įvertinant, ar kliente arba paslaugose padaryti keitimai lėmė kritinį vartotojo autentifikavimo patirties ir patikimumo suprastėjimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-576">Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

3) <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-577">Kai įvyksta triktis, šie signalai perduoda svarbius trikties kodus iš atsakingo komponento („Office“ kliento kodo, autentifikavimo bibliotekų arba tarnybų), kuriuos galima naudoti nustatant, diagnozuojant ir mažinant poveikį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-577">When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

4) <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-578">Šie signalai siunčiami į įvairias parengimo pateikti ir sveikatos stebėjimo programas, kurios suaktyvina įspėjimus, kad mūsų inžinieriai galėtų greitai imtis problemos sprendimo ir būtų greičiau sumažinta kritinių trikčių rizika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-578">These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors, which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-579">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-579">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-580">**Actiontype** – „oneauthtransaction“ yra vienintelė reikšmė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-580">**Actiontype** - "oneauthtransaction" is the only value.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-581">**Appaudience** – taikymo auditorija („Automation“, „Preproduction“ arba „Production“)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-581">**Appaudience** - Application audience (Automation, Preproduction, or Production)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-582">**Appname** – taikomosios programos pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-582">**Appname** - App name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-583">**Appver** – taikomosios programos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-583">**Appver** - App version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-584">**Authoutcome** – ar autentifikavimo bandymas pavyko, nepavyko, ar buvo atšauktas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-584">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-585">**Correlationid** – identifikatorius, naudojamas prijungti informaciją apie šį atskirą įvykį prie tarnybų duomenų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-585">**Correlationid** - Identifier used to join information regarding this individual event with services data</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-586">**Count** – kiek kartų įvyko klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-586">**Count** - Number of times the error occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-587">**Devicenetworkstate** – įrenginio tinklo būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-587">**Devicenetworkstate** - Device network state</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-588">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** – įrenginio profilio telemetrijos ID (eilutė, kurią naudoja MATS konkrečiam įrenginiui identifikuoti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-588">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Device profile telemetry ID (string used by MATS to identify a specific device)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-589">**duration_max** – maksimali šiame signale agreguotų operacijų trukmė, išreikšta milisekundėmis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-589">**duration_max** - Minimum duration, in milliseconds, of the transactions aggregated on this signal.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-590">**duration_min** – minimali šiame signale agreguotų operacijų trukmė, išreikšta milisekundėmis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-590">**duration_min** - Maximum duration, in milliseconds, of the transactions aggregated on this signal.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-591">**duration_sum** – šiame signale agreguotų operacijų trukmių suma, išreikšta milisekundėmis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-591">**duration_sum** - Sum of durations, in milliseconds, of the transactions aggregated on this signal.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-592">**Endtime** – „OneAuth“ operacijos pabaigos laikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-592">**Endtime** - Time at which the OneAuth transaction ended.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-593">**Error** – „OneAuth“ būsenos kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-593">**Error** - OneAuth status code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-594">**Eventtype** – įvykio tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-594">**Eventtype** - Event type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-595">**Issilent** – klaidinga, jei vartotojo sąsaja buvo rodoma; teisinga tai buvo fone vykstantis įvykis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-595">**Issilent** - False if UI was shown; true if it was a background event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-596">**oneauth_api** – nurodo, „OneAuth“ viešąjį API, kuris buvo iškviestas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-596">**oneauth_api** - Specifies the public API of OneAuth that was invoked.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-597">**oneauth_Domain** – jei API iškvietimas sukėlė klaida, tai yra šios klaidos sistemos domenas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-597">**oneauth_Domain** - If the API call resulted in an error, this is the system domain of that error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-598">**oneauth_ErrorCode** – klaidos kodas, žymintis „OneAuth“ vidinės klaidos būseną.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-598">**oneauth_ErrorCode** - Error code representing the internal error state for OneAuth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-599">Keičia seną oneauth_errortag lauką.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-599">Replaces the old oneauth_errortag field.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-600">**oneauth_errortag** – skaitinis identifikatorius kodo eilutei, atsakingai už klaidos generavimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-600">**oneauth_errortag** - Numerical identifier for a line of code that was responsible for generating an error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-601">**oneauth_ExecutionFlow** – žymų sekos, identifikuojančios kodo kelią, naudotą šio API iškvietimui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-601">**oneauth_ExecutionFlow** - A series of tags identifying the codepath this API invocation took.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-602">**oneauth_internalerror** – klaidos kodas, žymintis „OneAuth“ vidinės klaidos būseną.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-602">**oneauth_internalerror** - Error code representing the internal error state for OneAuth.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-603">**oneauth_ServerErrorCode** – serverio klaida grąžinta į „OneAuth“ baigiant šį API kvietimą, jei tokia įvyko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-603">**oneauth_ServerErrorCode** - The server error returned to OneAuth at the conclusion of this API call, if one was encountered.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-604">**oneauth_SystemErrorCode** – sistemos klaida grąžinta į „OneAuth“ baigiant šį API kvietimą, jei tokia įvyko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-604">**oneauth_SystemErrorCode** - The system error returned to OneAuth at the conclusion of this API call, if one was encountered.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-605">**oneauth_Tag** – „OneAuth“ žymė, nurodanti galutinę vietą kode, pasiektą baigus šį API kvietimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-605">**oneauth_Tag** - The OneAuth tag designating the final place in code reached at the conclusion of this API call.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-606">**oneauth_transactionuploadid** – nurodo atsitiktinai sugeneruotą vidinį GUID, kuris susiejamas su tam tikru „OneAuth“ API iškvietimu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-606">**oneauth_transactionuploadid** - Specifies the randomly generated internal GUID that maps to the specific invocation of a OneAuth API.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-607">**oneauth_version** – „OneAuth“ SDK versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-607">**oneauth_version** - The version of the OneAuth SDK.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-608">**Platform** – OS platforma (0: Win32, 1: „Android“, 2: „iOS“, 3: „macOS“, 4: „WinRT“)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-608">**Platform** - OS Platform (0: Win32, 1: Android, 2: iOS, 3: macOS, 4: WinRT</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-609">**Scenarioname** – scenarijaus, kuriam būtinas autentifikavimas, pavadinimas, nurodytas kviečiančios taikomosios programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-609">**Scenarioname** - Name of the scenario for which auth is necessary, specified by the calling application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-610">**Schemaver** – schemos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-610">**Schemaver** - Schema Version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-611">**Sdkver** –MATS sdk versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-611">**Sdkver** - Version of the MATS sdk</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-612">**Sessionid** – seanso ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-612">**Sessionid** - Session ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-613">**severityError** – svarba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-613">**severityError** - severity</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-614">**starttime** – „OneAuth“ operacijos pradžios laikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-614">**starttime** - Time at which the OneAuth transaction began.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-615">**Timestamp** – laiko žyma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-615">**Timestamp** - Timestamp</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-616">**Type** – klaidos tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-616">**Type** - Error type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-617">**Uploaded** – unikalus šio konkretaus įvykio identifikatorius, skirtas išvengti apgaulės.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-617">**Uploaded** - Unique identifier for this particular event, for de-duping purposes.</span></span>


### <a name="onenotesigninssoexternalappsaccountfound"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-618">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsAccountFound</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-618">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsAccountFound</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-619">Šis įvykis užregistruojamas, kai TokenSharingManager pateiktame paskyrų sąraše randama paskyra su galiojančiu atnaujinimo atpažinimo ženklu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-619">This event is logged when an account with a valid refresh token is found among the list of accounts provided by TokenSharingManager.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-620">Šis scenarijus būdingas bendrajai autentifikacijai (SSO).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-620">This scenario is specific to Single Sign-on (SSO).</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-621">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-621">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-622">**AccountType** – užregistruojamas paskyros tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-622">**AccountType** - Logs the type of account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-623">**ProviderPackageID** – užregistruojamas šią paskyrą pateikusios programos paketo ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-623">**ProviderPackageID** - Logs the package ID of the app that provided this account</span></span>

### <a name="onenotesigninssoexternalappsinvalidaccount"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-624">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsInvalidAccount</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-624">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsInvalidAccount</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-625">Šis įvykis užregistruojamas, kai įvyksta klaida bandant gauti TokenSharingManager pateiktame paskyrų sąraše esančios paskyros atnaujinimo atpažinimo ženklą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-625">This event is logged when there was an error when attempting to obtain a refresh token for an account in the list of accounts provided by TokenSharingManager.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-626">Šis scenarijus būdingas bendrajai autentifikacijai (SSO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-626">This scenario is specific to Single Sign-on (SSO)</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-627">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-627">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-628">**RawError** – užregistruojama pradinė klaida, gauta bandant gauti paskyros atnaujinimo atpažinimo ženklą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-628">**RawError** - Logs the raw error obtained when attempting to get a refresh token with the given account</span></span>
