### <a name="officeclicktorunbootstrapper"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-636">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-636">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-637">„Office“ nustatymų ir atsargų duomenys, renkami vartotojui paleidus „Office“ setup.exe, kad modifikuotų įdiegtus „Office“ produktus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-637">Office set up and inventory data collected when the user is running Office setup.exe to modify their installed Office products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-638">Naudojami vertinant viso vartotojo inicijuoto „Office“ diegimo sėkmingumą, įskaitant būtinųjų sąlygų patikras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-638">Used to measure success / failure of a full user-initiated Office installation including pre-requisite checks.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-639">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-639">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-640">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – įvykusios klaidos kodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-640">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – The error code we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-641">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – funkcija, kurios klaida įvyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-641">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – The function we failed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-642">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – įkėlimo įrankio dalis, kurioje įvyko klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-642">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – The part that we failed in the boostrapperbootstrapper</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-643">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – išimties tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-643">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – The type of exception we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-644">**Data\_Culture** – kultūra, su kuria vykdomas šis „exe“, pvz., „en-us“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-644">**Data\_Culture** - the culture we are running this exe with, i.e. en-us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-645">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** – atpažinimo ženklo SHA-256 maiša, kurią mums nurodo OLS paslauga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-645">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** - a sha-256 hash of a token the OLS service gives us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-646">**Data\_Platform** – „x64“ arba „x86“ įdiegtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-646">**Data\_Platform** - x64 or x86 install</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-647">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – įvykusi būtinųjų sąlygų triktis, pvz., nepalaikoma operacinė sistema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-647">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – The prerequisite failure we hit, i.e. the operating system is not supported</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-648">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** – diegiamas produktas, pvz., „Microsoft 365“ programos įmonėms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-648">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** - Product we're installing, i.e. Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktoruncorruptioncheck"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-649">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-649">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-650">„Office“ sąrankos ir inventoriaus duomenys, renkami Spustelėkite ir naudokitės klientui vykdant patikrą dėl sugadinimo, siekiant įsitikinti, kad „Office“ dvejetainiai failai yra teisingi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-650">Office set up and inventory data collected when Click-to-Run client is running a corruption check to make sure that Office binaries are correct.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-651">Naudojami vertinant „Office“ dvejetainių failų sugadinimą ir kurie dvejetainiai failai yra sugadinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-651">Used to measure corruption of Office binaries, and which binaries are corrupt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-652">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-652">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-653">**Data\_Active –** dabartinė srauto deklaracija, kurią tikriname diske</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-653">**Data\_Active -** The current stream manifest we're checking on disk</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-654">**Data\_ActivePackages –** kokie paketai yra deklaracijoje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-654">**Data\_ActivePackages -** what packages the manifest contains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-655">**Data\_ActiveVersion –** deklaracijos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-655">**Data\_ActiveVersion -** the version of the manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-656">**Data\_AddFileCount –** kiek failų įtraukiame</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-656">**Data\_AddFileCount -** how many files we're adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-657">**Data\_AddFileFiles –** įtraukiamų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-657">**Data\_AddFileFiles -** a sample of the files we're adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-658">**Data\_CompressionLevel –** kaip failai suglaudinti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-658">**Data\_CompressionLevel -** how the files are compressed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-659">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel –** kaip nuodugniai tikriname dėl sugadinimo (etapai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-659">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel -** how deeply we're checking for corruption, stages</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-660">**Data\_CorruptSizeCount –** kelių failų dydis yra sugadintas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-660">**Data\_CorruptSizeCount -** how many files have a corrupt size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-661">**Data\_CorruptSizeFiles –** failų, kurių dydis sugadintas, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-661">**Data\_CorruptSizeFiles -** a sample of the files that have a corrupted size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-662">**Data\_CorruptVersionCount –** kelių failų versija sugadinta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-662">**Data\_CorruptVersionCount -** how many files have a corrupted version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-663">**Data\_CorruptVersionFiles –** failų, kurių versija sugadinta, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-663">**Data\_CorruptVersionFiles -** a sample of the files that have a corrupted version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-664">**Data\_FileBadDigestCount –** kiek failų nepavyko atidaryti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-664">**Data\_FileBadDigestCount -** how many files we failed to open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-665">**Data\_FileBadDigestFiles –** failų, kurių nepavyko atidaryti, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-665">**Data\_FileBadDigestFiles -** a sample of the files that we were unable to open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-666">**Data\_FileNotSignedCount –** kiek failų nėra pasirašyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-666">**Data\_FileNotSignedCount -** have many files that aren't signed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-667">**Data\_FileNotSignedFiles –** failų, kurie nėra pasirašyti, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-667">**Data\_FileNotSignedFiles -** a sample of the files that aren't signed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-668">**Data\_FileNotTrustedCount –** kiek failų nėra patikimi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-668">**Data\_FileNotTrustedCount -** how many files aren't trusted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-669">**Data\_FileNotTrustedFiles –** nepatikimų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-669">**Data\_FileNotTrustedFiles -** a sample of the files that we don't trust</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-670">**Data\_IncompleteFileCount –** kiek failų atrodo nepilni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-670">**Data\_IncompleteFileCount -** how many files seem to be incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-671">**Data\_IncompleteFileFiles –** nepilnų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-671">**Data\_IncompleteFileFiles -** a sample of the files that are incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-672">**Data\_KeepFileCount –** dėl kiek failų nieko nedaroma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-672">**Data\_KeepFileCount -** how many files we're not doing anything to</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-673">**Data\_KeepFileFiles –** paliekamų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-673">**Data\_KeepFileFiles -** a sample of files we're keeping</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-674">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileCount –** kiek failų nekeičiama, nepaisant to, kad jie yra nepilni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-674">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileCount -** how many files we're not changing despite them being incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-675">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileFiles –** paliekamų nepilnų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-675">**Data\_KeepIncompleteFileFiles -** a sample of the files we're keeping that are incomplete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-676">**Data\_MismatchSizeCount –** kelių failų dydis neatitinka mūsų deklaracijos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-676">**Data\_MismatchSizeCount -** how many files have a size that doesn't match our manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-677">**Data\_MismatchSizeFiles –** failų, kurių dydis neatitinka, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-677">**Data\_MismatchSizeFiles -** a sample of the files that are mismatched in size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-678">**Data\_MismatchVersionCount –** kelių failų versija skiriasi nuo mūsų deklaracijos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-678">**Data\_MismatchVersionCount -** how many files that have a version different than our manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-679">**Data\_MismatchVersionFiles –** failų, kurių versijos neatitinka, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-679">**Data\_MismatchVersionFiles -** a sample of the files that have mismatched versions</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-680">**Data\_MissingFileCount –** kiek failų trūksta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-680">**Data\_MissingFileCount -** how many files seem to be missing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-681">**Data\_MissingFileFiles –** trūkstamų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-681">**Data\_MissingFileFiles -** a sample of the files that are missing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-682">**Data\_NotToBeStreamedFileCount –** kiek failų neperduodama srautu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-682">**Data\_NotToBeStreamedFileCount -** how many files we're not streaming</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-683">**Data\_RemoveFileCount –** kiek failų šalinama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-683">**Data\_RemoveFileCount -** how many files we're removing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-684">**Data\_RemoveFileFiles –** šalinamų failų imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-684">**Data\_RemoveFileFiles -** a sample of the files we're removing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-685">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchCount –** kiek failų vienetų neatitinka deklaracijos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-685">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchCount -** how many files have units that don't match the manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-686">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchFiles –** failų, kurių srauto vienetai neatitinka, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-686">**Data\_StreamUnitsMismatchFiles -** a sample of the files that have a stream with units mismatched</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-687">**Data\_TimeElapsed –** kiek užtruko patikra dėl sugadinimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-687">**Data\_TimeElapsed -** how long we took to check for corruption</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-688">**Data\_UpdateFileCount –** kiek failų naujiname</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-688">**Data\_UpdateFileCount -** how many files we're updating</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-689">**Data\_UpdateFileFiles –** failų, kuriuos įtraukiame, imtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-689">**Data\_UpdateFileFiles -** a sample of the files we're adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-690">**Data\_Working –** nauja tikrinama deklaracija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-690">**Data\_Working -** the new manifest we're checking</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-691">**Data\_WorkingVersion –** naujos deklaracijos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-691">**Data\_WorkingVersion -** the version of the new manifest</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-703">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-703">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-704">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode –** įvykusios klaidos kodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-704">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode-** The error code we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-705">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource –** funkcija, kurios klaida įvyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-705">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource-** The function we failed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-706">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState –** įkėlimo įrankio dalis, kurioje įvyko klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-706">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState-** The part that we failed in the boot-strapper</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-707">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType –** išimties tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-707">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType-** The type of exception we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-708">**Data\_ConfigurationHost –** pagrindinis kompiuteris, iš kurio gautas configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-708">**Data\_ConfigurationHost-** The host where the configuration.xml came from</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-709">**Data\_ConfigurationId –** iš configuration.xml gautas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-709">**Data\_ConfigurationId-** The ID we get from a configuration.xml</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-710">**Data\_ConfigurationSource –** iš kur gautas configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-710">**Data\_ConfigurationSource-** We the configuration.xml came from</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-711">**Data\_Culture –** kultūra, su kuria vykdomas šis „exe“, pvz., „en-us“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-711">**Data\_Culture-** the culture we are running this exe with, i.e. en-us</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunrepomanlogger"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-720">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-720">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-721">Ataskaitos apie naujo spustelėkite ir naudokitės naujinimo srauto būseną („Repoman“) ir ar ji sėkmingai atsisiunčia ir pritaiko „Office" naujinimus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-721">Reports on the status for the new Click-to-Run update pipeline ("Repoman") and if it successfully downloads and applies Office updates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-722">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-722">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-723">**ApplySucceeded –** tiesa, jei srautui sėkmingai pritaikytas „Office“ naujinys, klaidinga, jei ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-723">**ApplySucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully applied an Office update, false if not.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-724">**DownloadSucceeded –** tiesa, jei srautui sėkmingai pritaikytas „Office“ naujinys, klaidinga, jei ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-724">**DownloadSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully downloaded an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-725">**ErrorCode –** paskutinės klaidos, kuri įvyko „spustelėkite ir naudokitės“ „Repoman“ sraute, kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-725">**ErrorCode -** The code of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-726">**ErrorDetails –** papildoma paskutinės klaidos, kuri įvyko „spustelėkite ir naudokitės“ „Repoman“ sraute, informacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-726">**ErrorDetails -**  Additional error details of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-727">**ErrorMessage –** paskutinės klaidos, kuri įvyko „spustelėkite ir naudokitės“ „Repoman“ sraute, pranešimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-727">**ErrorMessage -** The message of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-728">**Openstreamsessionpavyko –** teisinga, jei srautas sėkmingai sukuria seansą, skirtą „Office“ naujiniui transliuoti, klaidinga, jei ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-728">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully creates a session for streaming an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-729">**RepomanErrorMessage –** klaidos pranešimas, gautas iš repoman.dll.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-729">**RepomanErrorMessage -** The error message received from the repoman.dll.</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktoruntransportexperimentaltransportpipelinecreatetransport"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1685">Office.ClickToRun.Transport.ExperimentalTransport.PipelineCreateTransport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1685">Office.ClickToRun.Transport.ExperimentalTransport.PipelineCreateTransport</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1686">„Office“ sąrankos ir inventoriaus duomenys, renkami, kai Spustelėkite ir naudokitės klientas kuria perdavimo srautą, kad atsisiųstų „Office“ failus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1686">Office set up and inventory data collected when the Click-to-Run client is creating a transport stream to download Office files.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1687">Naudojami nustatant įvairių perdavimo technologijų (pvz., HTTP, BITS, DO) sveikatą. Tai svarbu, kad „Office“ būtų tinkamai atsisiųsta diegiant ir naujinant.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1687">Used for determining the health of various transport technologies (e.g., HTTP, BITS, DO) which is critical to downloading Office properly for installation and updates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1688">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1688">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1807">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1807">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1808">*[Šis įvykis buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ komponavimo versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse komponavimo versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1808">*[This event has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1809">Šis įvykis naudojamas gauti standartinius meta duomenis kiekvieno Inventory priedo paleidimo metu, kuris yra dalis „Office“ aptarnavimo tvarkytuvo bei naudojamas „Office“ atsargų informacijai tuose kompiuteriuose, kur IT administratorius pasirinko dalyvauti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1809">This event is used to acquire standard metadata on each run of the Inventory add-on, which is part of the Office Serviceability Manager and is used for inventory Office information on those machines for which an IT admin has opted in.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1810">Specifinio intereso meta duomenys čia yra sesijos ID. Jie naudojami norint susieti kitus duomenis, saugomus kiekvieno nuomininko debesies tarnyboje. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1810">The metadata of specific interest here is the session ID, and it is used for linking to other data stored within a per-tenant cloud service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1811">Šis įvykis neturi papildomų laukų, kadangi yra reikalingi tik meta duomenys.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1811">This event contains no extra fields since only the metadata is relevant.</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1812">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1812">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1813">Šis įvykis užregistruojamas, kai tinklo tarnyba iškviečiama iš Spustelėkite ir naudokitės aptarnavimo tvarkytuvo atsargų papildinio, nesvarbu, ar iškvietimas sėkmingas, ar ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1813">This event is logged when the call to the webservice made within the Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager Inventory add-on completes, irrespective of whether it succeeds or fails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1814">Iš esmės tai paskutinė operacija papildinyje, pagal kurią stebima bendroji operacijos būsena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1814">This is essentially the last operation within the add-on to track the overall operation status.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1815">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1815">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1816">**ActionDetail**-papildoma informacija apie klaidos laiką.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1816">**ActionDetail** -  Additional details for when a failure occurs.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1817">Jei HTTP užklausa pavyksta, ActionDetail bus 0.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1817">If the HTTP request succeeds, ActionDetail will be 0.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1818">Jei laukas Rezultatas nėra tinkamas (t. y. ne 0), vadinasi užklausa nėra išsiųsta, šis laukas užregistruos vidinės klaidos kodą, kuris yra toks pat, kaip laukas Rezultatas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1818">If the Result field is not OK (i.e. not 0), which means that the request is not sent, this field will log the internal error code which is the same as the Result field.</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerwebservicefailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1831">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1831">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1832">Šis įvykis užregistruojamas, kai nepavyksta iškviesti tinklo tarnybos iš „Office“ aptarnavimo tvarkytuvo papildinio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1832">Whenever a call to a webservice within one of the Office Serviceability Manager add-ins fails, this statement is logged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1833">Triktys gali būti dėl vidinių gedimų arba negalėjimo prisijungti prie tinklo tarnybos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1833">Failures can be due to internal failures or an inability to connect to the webservice.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1834">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1834">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1835">**Add-on** – Spustelėkite ir naudokitės aptarnavimo tvarkytuvo papildinys, iš kurio buvo iškviesta tinklo tarnyba.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1835">**Add-on** - The Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager add-on from which the webservice call was made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1836">Tai gali būti tokios reikšmės kaip atsargos, valdymas ir pan., užkoduotos kaip skaitinės reikšmės.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1836">This can have values like inventory, manageability, etc. encoded as a numeric value.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1837">**Correlation ID** – atsitiktiniu būdu sugeneruotas GUID, būdingas dabartiniam egzemplioriui, kuris siunčiamas į tinklo tarnybą kliento ir serverio iškvietimams susieti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1837">**Correlation ID** - A randomly generated GUID specific to the current instance that is sent to the webservice to correlate calls between the client and the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1838">**ErrorInfo** – skaitinių klaidos kodų informacija, kurią pateikia „Office“ tinklo tarnybos iškvietimo API.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1838">**ErrorInfo** - Numeric error code information returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1839">**ErrorMessage** – pranešimas, pateikiantis daugiau įžvalgų apie gedimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1839">**ErrorMessage** - A message providing further insight into the failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1840">Kiekviena klaidos tipas susiejamas su užprogramuota eilute; kai kurie klaidų tipai susiejami su galimai keliomis eilutėmis, atsižvelgiant į konkretų gedimo pobūdį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1840">Each error type maps to a hardcoded string, with some error types mapping to potentially multiple strings depending on the specific nature of the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1841">**Function** – funkcija kode, iš kurios įvykdytas dabartinis iškvietimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1841">**Function** - The function in the code from which the current call occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1842">**Status** – HTTP būsenos kodas, kurį iškvietimas pateikia tinklo tarnybai, pvz., 404, 500 ir pan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1842">**Status** - The HTTP status code returned by the call to the webservice, e.g. 404, 500, etc.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1900">Šio produkto telemetrija renkama vidinės operacijos statuso stebėjimui ir įrašymui, taip pat derinimo informacijai, kad būtų pagerintas patikimumas ir efektyvumas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1900">This product telemetry is collected for tracking and logging the internal transaction status and reconciliation information to improve reliability and performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1901">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis analizei ir vidinės operacijos apdorojimo ir derinimo mechanizmų patikimumo ir efektyvumo gerinimui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1901">Microsoft uses this data to analyze and improve the reliability and performance of the internal transaction processing and reconciliation mechanisms.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1902">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1902">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1903">**MicrosoftPurchaseOrderId** - „Microsoft“ užsakymo ID atsiųstas Mažmeninės prekybos federacijos tarnybos (RFS) stebėjimo tikslams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1903">**MicrosoftPurchaseOrderId** - Microsoft Order Id sent by Retail Federation Service (RFS) for tracking purposes.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1904">**ResponseCode** - HTTP atsako kodas (int)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1904">**ResponseCode** - HTTP Response code (int)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1905">**StatusCode** - RFS (mažmeninės prekybos federacijos tarnybos) atsako statuso kodas (RFS apibrėžtas išvard. int- ribotas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1905">**StatusCode** - RFS response status code (RFS defined Enum int- finite)</span></span>


### <a name="officeandroiddocsuipaywallcontrolseeallfeaturesanalytics"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1906">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.SeeAllFeaturesAnalytics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1906">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.SeeAllFeaturesAnalytics</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1907">Renkame šią naudojimo telemetriją norėdami sužinoti, kiek laiko vartotojas praleidžia ekrane „Rodyti daugiau pranašumų“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1907">We collect this usage telemetry to see how much time the user spends on the “See more benefits” screen.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1908">Duomenys naudojami norint suprasti ypatybės „žr. daugiau pranašumų“ naudojimą, kad būtų galima dar labiau optimizuoti būsimųjų versijų naudojimo funkcijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1908">The data is used to understand usage of the “See more benefits” feature and further optimize the experience in future versions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1909">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1909">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1910">**Duration** – ilgasis sveikasis skaičius, nurodantis laiką, kurį vartotojas praleido ekrane „Rodyti visas funkcijas“, išreikštas milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1910">**Duration** - Long integer indicating time spent by user on “See All Features” screen in milliseconds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1911">**EventDate** – įvykio įvykimo laiko žyma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1911">**EventDate** - Timestamp of the event occurrence</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1912">**MostExplored** – sveikasis skaičius, žymintis labiausiai perjungto elemento indeksą „Microsoft 365“ programų ir jų funkcijų sąraše</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1912">**MostExplored** - Integer denoting the index of the most toggled item in a list of Microsoft 365 apps and their features</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1913">**SessionID** – globaliai unikalus identifikatorius (GUID), kad galima būtų sujungti įvykius pagal seansą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1913">**SessionID** - Globally Unique Identifier (GUID) to connect events by session</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroiddocsuipaywallcontrolskuchooseranalytics"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1914">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.SkuChooserAnalytics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1914">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.SkuChooserAnalytics</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1918">**Duration** – ilgasis sveikasis skaičius, nurodantis laiką, kurį vartotojas praleido Sku parinkiklio ekrane, išreikštas milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1918">**Duration** – Long integer indicating time spent by user on Sku Chooser screen in milliseconds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1919">**EventDate** – įvykio įvykimo laiko žyma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1919">**EventDate** – Timestamp of the event occurrence</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroiddocsuiviewsdimeerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1921">Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.DimeError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1921">Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.DimeError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1922">Šis įvykis renkamas „Office“ programai, skirtai „Android“ (išleista „Huawei“ ir Kinijos parduotuvėse).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1922">This event is collected for the Office app for Android (released on Huawei and in China Stores).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1923">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad bandymas įsigyti „Microsoft 365“ prenumeratą per „Dime“ (webURL, įkeltą į kliento žiniatinklio rodinį) nepavyko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1923">This event indicates that an attempt to purchase a Microsoft 365 subscription through Dime (a webURL loaded in client webview) has failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1924">Fiksuojami tik klaidų scenarijai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1924">Only the error scenarios are captured.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1925">Šie įvykių duomenys yra tik klaidų duomenys ir yra naudojami siekiant užtikrinti „Dime“ pirkimo srauto sveikatą kliente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1925">This event data is error data only and is used to ensure the health of the Dime purchase flow in the client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1926">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1926">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1927">**CorrelationID** – ID, kuris unikaliai identifikuoja „Dime“ pirkimo seansą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1927">**CorrelationID** - ID that uniquely identifies a Dime purchase session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1928">**ErrorReason** – nurodo įvykusios klaidos priežastį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1928">**ErrorReason** - Indicates the reason for the error that happened.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1929">0 – nežinoma klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1929">0 – Unknown error</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1930">1 – internetas nepasiekiamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1930">1 – Internet not available</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1931">2 – universalaus unikaliojo identifikatoriaus (UUID) tikrinimas nepavyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1931">2 – Universally unique identifier (UUID) validation failed</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1932">3 – universalus unikalusis identifikatorius (UUID) neapibrėžtas arba tuščias</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1932">3 - Universally unique identifier (UUID) is null or empty</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1933">4 – „JavaScript“ įterpimo klaida, dėl kurios „Office“ programa, skirta „Android“, negali perduoti „authToken“ į „Dime“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1933">4 – JavaScript injection error where the Office app for Android can’t pass authToken to Dime</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1934">5 – bazinis „WebURL“, įkeltas kliente, yra neleistinas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1934">5 – Base WebURL loaded on client is invalid</span></span>


### <a name="officeandroiddocsuiviewspremiumfeatureupsell"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1935">Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.PremiumFeatureUpsell</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1935">Office.Android.DocsUI.Views.PremiumFeatureUpsell</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1936">Šis įvykis užfiksuoja nemokamus vartotojų paspaudimus, kai jie nori peržiūrėti mokamos prieigos prie informacijos funkciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1936">This event captures clicks by a free user clicks to view a feature behind the pay wall.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1937">Duomenys naudojami norint įvertinti vartotojų sąveiką su kontekstine papildomo pardavimo patirtimi ir suprasti funkcijas, kurioms vartotojas teikia pirmenybę, skatinančias juos pirkti prenumeratą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1937">The data is used to measure the interaction of users with the contextual upsell experience and understand which features are preferred by the user which drives them to buy a subscription.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1938">Tai padeda mums investuoti, kad pagerintume pageidaujamą įeities taškų rinkinį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1938">This helps us invest to improve those preferred set of entry points.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1939">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1939">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1940">**featureId** – TCID (įrankių juostos valdiklio identifikatorius) skirtas aukščiausios kokybės („Premium“) funkcijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1940">**featureId** - TCID for premium feature</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1941">**featureName** – Aukščiausios kokybės („Premium“) funkcijos pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1941">**featureName** - Premium Feature Title</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1942">**seePlanButtonClick** – Kiek kartų spustelėjama ant „Žr. plano mygtukus“, kai papildomai parduodama vartotojo sąsaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1942">**seePlanButtonClick** - How many times “See plan buttons” gets clicked in upsell UI</span></span>

### <a name="officeappleiapreviewyoursubscriptionios"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1943">Office.Apple.IAPReviewYourSubscriptioniOS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1943">Office.Apple.IAPReviewYourSubscriptioniOS</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1944">Šis įvykis užfiksuoja seanso metaduomenis, kai vartotojui rodoma pirkimo programoje (IAP) vartotojo sąsaja ir mygtukai, su kuriais vėliau vartotojas sąveikauja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1944">This event captures session-based metadata when the In-App-Purchase (IAP) UI is shown to the user and the buttons the user subsequently interacts with.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1945">Šie duomenys naudojami mums padėti suprasti pirkimo srauto trintį ir palyginti jį su kitos pirkimo patirties piltuvėliu, kad suprastume, kuri patirtis yra geresnė vartotojui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1945">This data is used to help us understand the friction in the purchase flow and compare it with the funnel of a different purchase experience to understand which experience is better for the user.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1946">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1946">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1947">**FlowType** – Sveikasis skaičius – Srautas iš ten, kur paleista IAP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1947">**FlowType** - Integer – Flow from where IAP was launched.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1948">**Restore** – Eilutė – taisyklės žyma įrašoma, kai spustelėjamas atkūrimo mygtukas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1948">**Restore** - String – rule tag is logged when restore button is clicked</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1949">**PremiumFeatures** – Eilutė – taisyklės žyma registruojama, kai spustelėjamas „PremiumFeatures“ mygtukas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1949">**PremiumFeatures** - String – rule tag is logged when “PremiumFeatures” button is clicked</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1950">**Product** – Eilutė – Vartotojų pasirinktas SKU</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1950">**Product** - String - The SKU selected by the users</span></span>


### <a name="officeappleinapppurchasecontext"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1951">Office.Apple.InAppPurchaseContext</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1951">Office.Apple.InAppPurchaseContext</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1952">Šis įvykis įvertina kritinę naudojimo telemetriją pirkimo programos ekrano įeities taške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1952">This event measures critical usage telemetry for the point of entry of the in-app purchase screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1953">Duomenys padeda suprasti ir pagerinti vartotojo patirtį nustatant pageidaujamą įeities tašką pirkimo programoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1953">The data helps understand and improve the user experience by identifying the preferred entry point for an in-app purchase.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-1955">**context** – Eilutė – Srautas, per kurį vartotojas pateko į pirkimo programoje puslapį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-1955">**context** - String – The flow through which the user landed on the in app purchase page</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingfullvalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2084">Office.Licensing.FullValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2084">Office.Licensing.FullValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2085">Renkama kiekviename seanse, kuriame pranešama kompiuterio licencijavimo būsena ir vartotojo matomos klaidos, dėl kurių jis negali naudoti programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2085">This is collected on every session that reports the licensing state of the machine and reports the errors that the user is seeing due to which they are not able to use the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2086">Šis įvykis nurodo, ar vartotojo kompiuterio sveikata gera, ar ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2086">This event indicates if the user's machine is healthy or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2087">Šio įvykio anomalijų aptikimo funkcija nurodo, ar netinkamą vartotojo elgseną kelia veikimo suprastėjimas, ar aktyvinimo mechanizmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2087">We have anomaly detection set up for this event to indicate if a regression or activation mechanism is causing bad user behavior.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2088">Tai taip pat svarbu diagnozuojant vartotojo problemas ir stebint sistemos sveikatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2088">This is also critical when diagnosing user issues and for monitoring system health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2089">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2089">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2090">**Acid** – GUID identifikatorius, nurodantis „Office“ produktą, kurio licencija suteikta vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2090">**Acid** – A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2091">**ActivationAttributes** – vartotojo naudojamo aktyvinimo mechanizmo tipas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2091">**ActivationAttributes** - Type of activation mechanism that the user is using.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2092">**IsSessionLicensing** – ar šiuo metu vykdomas bendrai naudojamo kompiuterio aktyvinimo režimas, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2092">**IsSessionLicensing** – Whether we are currently running under shared computer activation mode or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2093">**LicenseCategory** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, kategorija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2093">**LicenseCategory** – Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2094">**Licenses** – visų „Office“ licencijų, kurios yra kompiuteryje, pavadinimų sąrašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2094">**Licenses** – List of names of all the  Office licenses that are present on the machine</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2095">**LicenseStatuses** – visų „Office“ licencijų, kurios yra kompiuteryje, būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2095">**LicenseStatuses** – Status of all the Office licenses present on the machine</span></span> 

### <a name="officelicensinggetentitlement"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2096">Office.Licensing.GetEntitlement</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2096">Office.Licensing.GetEntitlement</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2097">Renkame, kai vartotojas nustato įrenginį, ir iškviečiame licencijavimo paslaugą, kad aptiktume, ar prisijungęs vartotojas turi teisę naudotis „Office“, ar ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2097">We collect this when the user is setting up a device and we call our licensing service to detect if the logged in user has an Office entitlement or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2098">Tai praneša apie to iškvietimo rezultatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2098">This reports the result of that call.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2099">Tai svarbu nustatant, ar vartotojo būsena yra tinkama ir jam veikia visos funkcijos, taip pat naudojama sistemos sveikatos ir diagnostikos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2099">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2100">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2100">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2101">**EntitlementCount** – vartotojo turimų teisių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2101">**EntitlementCount** – Number of entitlements the user has</span></span>


### <a name="officelicensingheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2102">Office.Licensing.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2102">Office.Licensing.Heartbeat</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2103">Kiekviename seanse tikriname, ar praėjo 72 valandos nuo paskutinio licencijos atnaujinimo, ir bandome pratęsti dabartinės licencijos galiojimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2103">On every session, we check if 72 hours have passed since the last license renewal and try to extend the expiry of the current license.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2104">Šis įvykis praneša, ar sėkmingas iškvietimas, kurį atlikome, siekdami užtikrinti, kad galime pratęsti licencijos galiojimą ir kad vartotojo „Office“ įdiegtis yra veikianti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2104">This event reports the success or failure of the call that we make to ensure we can extend the expiry of the license and keep the user's Office installation functional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2105">Tai svarbu diagnozuojant vartotojo su prenumerata susijusias ir paslaugų problemas, taip pat aptinkant veikimo suprastėjimą jau prenumeratą suaktyvinusiems vartotojams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2105">It is critical in diagnosing subscription-related issues and service issues for the user and is critical in detecting regressions for already activated subscription users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2106">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2106">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2107">**Mode** – numeris, nurodantis šiame kompiuteryje naudojamą „Office“ licencijavimo procesą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2107">**Mode** – An enumerator representation of the Office licensing stack that is being used on this machine</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2113">**ErrorType** – trikties priežastis, pvz., AlreadyRedeemedByOther.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2113">**ErrorType** - Reason of failure, such as "AlreadyRedeemedByOther".</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2137">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2137">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2138">**Acid** – GUID identifikatorius, nurodantis „Office“ produktą, kurio licencija suteikta vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2138">**Acid** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensinglicensingbar"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2141">Office.Licensing.LicensingBar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2141">Office.Licensing.LicensingBar</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2157">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2157">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2158">**FederationProvider** – eilutė, kurioje identifikuojamas šiuo metu prisijungusio vartotojo susiejimo teikėjas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2158">**FederationProvider** – A string that identifies the federation provider for the currently logged in user</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2163">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2163">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2164">**Acid** – GUID identifikatorius, nurodantis „Office“ produktą, kurio licencija suteikta vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2164">**Acid** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingnulfetcherfetchmodelfromols"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2170">Office.Licensing.Nul.Fetcher.FetchModelFromOls</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2170">Office.Licensing.Nul.Fetcher.FetchModelFromOls</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2171">Kai įrenginiui taikomas šiuolaikinis licencijavimo procesas, bandome gauti licencijos failą tiesiai iš paslaugos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2171">When the device is on the modern licensing stack, we try to get a license file directly from the service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2172">Šis įvykis praneša apie sėkmingą įvykdymą arba triktį kartu su paslaugos iškvietimo klaidos kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2172">This event reports the success or failure along with the error code of that service call.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2173">Tai svarbu nustatant, ar vartotojo būsena šiuolaikiniame licencijavimo procese yra tinkama, taip pat naudojama sistemos sveikatos ir diagnostikos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2173">It is critical to detect if the user is in a good state on the modern licensing stack, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2174">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2174">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2175">**MetadataValidationResult** – licencijos metaduomenų patikrinimo, siekiant patvirtinti, kad licencija nėra piktavališkai pakeista, rezultatas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2175">**MetadataValidationResult** – Result of the validation of the metadata of the license to verify that it has not been tampered with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2176">**SignatureValidationResult** – licencijos parašo patikrinimo, siekiant patvirtinti, kad licencija nėra piktavališkai pakeista, rezultatas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2176">**SignatureValidationResult** – Result of the validation of the signature of the license to verify that it has not been tampered with</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingnulvalidationfullvalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2177">Office.Licensing.Nul.Validation.FullValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2177">Office.Licensing.Nul.Validation.FullValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2178">Renkama kiekviename įrenginio, kuriam taikomas šiuolaikinis licencijavimo procesas, seanse.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2178">This is collected on every session of a device that is running on the modern licensing stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2179">Ji pranešama kompiuterio licencijavimo būseną ir vartotojo matomas klaidas, dėl kurių jis negali naudoti taikomosios programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2179">It reports the licensing state of the machine and reports the errors that the user is seeing due to which they are not able to use the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2180">Šis įvykis nurodo, ar vartotojo kompiuterio sveikata gera šiuolaikiniame licencijavimo procese.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2180">This event indicates if the user's machine is healthy on the modern licensing stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2181">Šio įvykio anomalijų aptikimo funkcija nurodo, ar netinkamą vartotojo elgseną kelia veikimo suprastėjimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2181">We have anomaly detection set up for this event to indicate if a regression is causing bad user behavior.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2182">Tai taip pat svarbu diagnozuojant vartotojo problemas ir stebint sistemos sveikatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2182">This is also critical when diagnosing user issues and for monitoring system health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2183">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2183">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2184">**Acid** – GUID identifikatorius, nurodantis „Office“ produktą, kurio licencija suteikta vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2184">**Acid** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2185">**AllAcids** – visų produkto, kurio licenciją vartotojas šiuo metu turi, GUID sąrašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2185">**AllAcids** – List of all the GUIDs of the product that the user is currently licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2186">**Category** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, kategorija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2186">**Category** - Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2187">**DaysRemaining** – iki dabartinės „Office“ licencijos galiojimo pabaigos likusių dienų skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2187">**DaysRemaining** – Number of days remaining before the current Office license expires</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2188">**LicenseId** – vartotojui išduotos licencijos iš raidžių ir skaitmenų sudarytas identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2188">**LicenseId** – An alphanumeric identifier of the license that was issued to the user</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2189">**LicenseType** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2189">**LicenseType** - Type of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

### <a name="officelicensingofficeclientlicensingdolicensevalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2190">Office.Licensing.OfficeClientLicensing.DoLicenseValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2190">Office.Licensing.OfficeClientLicensing.DoLicenseValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2191">Licencijavimo metaduomenys, renkami iš įrenginio per kiekvieną įkrovą, kurie praneša licencijos ACID, licencijos būseną, tipą ir kitas licencijos ypatybes, kurios svarbios identifikuojant vartotojui pasiekiamų funkcijų rinkinį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2191">This is licensing metadata that is collected from the device on every boot that reports the license acid, license status, type and other properties of the license that are critical in identifying the features set available to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2192">Tai svarbu identifikuojant vartotojui pasiekiamų funkcijų rinkinį ir vartotojui trūkstamas funkcijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2192">This is critical in identifying the feature set available to the user and if any functionality is missing for the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2193">Tai taip pat naudojama apskaičiuojant dienos / mėnesio aktyvių vartotojų skaičių ir pateikiant įvairias kitas ataskaitas įvairioms „Office“ komandoms, nes tai praneša vartotojo naudojamo produkto tipą, ar tai produkto prenumerata ir ar jam netrūksta svarbių funkcijų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2193">It is also used for Daily active users/Monthly active user calculations and various other reports by various teams across Office as this tells the type product that the user is using, whether it is a subscription product and whether they are missing any critical functionality.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2194">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2194">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2195">**FullValidationMode** – režimas, nurodantis, kad vykdomas išsamus licencijos patikrinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2195">**FullValidationMode** – Mode indicating that we are in full validation of license verification</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2196">**IsRFM** – nurodo, ar vartotojas dirba sumažinto funkcionalumo režimu, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2196">**IsRFM** – Indicates whether the user is in reduced functionality mode or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2197">**IsSCA** – nurodoma, ar veikia bendrai naudojamo kompiuterio aktyvinimo režimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2197">**IsSCA** – Indicates whether we are running in Shared computer activation mode</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2198">**IsSubscription** – nurodo, ar vartotojas naudoja prenumeratos licenciją, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2198">**IsSubscription** – Indicates whether the user is using a subscription license or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2199">**IsvNext** – nurodo ar naudojame naują šiuolaikinį licencijavimo procesą, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2199">**IsvNext** – Indicates whether we are using the new modern licensing stack or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2200">**LicenseCategory** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, kategorija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2200">**LicenseCategory** - Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2201">**LicenseStatus** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2201">**LicenseStatus** – Status of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2202">**LicenseType** – „Office“ licencijos, kurią naudoja vartotojas, tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2202">**LicenseType** - Type of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2203">**LicensingACID** – GUID identifikatorius, nurodantis „Office“ produktą, kurio licencija suteikta vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2203">**LicensingACID** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2204">**OlsLicenseId** – vartotojui išduotos licencijos iš raidžių ir skaitmenų sudarytas identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2204">**OlsLicenseId** - An alphanumeric identifier of the license that was issued to the user</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2205">**SkuIdIsNull** – nurodo, ar įvyko klaida ir nežinome, kokį produktą naudoja vartotojas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2205">**SkuIdIsNull** – Indicates whether we encountered an error and don't know the product that the user is running</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2206">**SlapiIsNull** – nurodo, ar kilo problema kuriant vieną iš licencijavimo objektų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2206">**SlapiIsNull** – Indicates whether we encountered a problem in populating one of the licensing objects</span></span>
