<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2210">Šis įvykis nerenka jokių laukų duomenų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2210">This event collects no fields.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingoobetrybuychoice"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2211">Office.Licensing.OOBE.TryBuyChoice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2211">Office.Licensing.OOBE.TryBuyChoice</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2212">Vartotojams, kurių naujuose įrenginiuose „Office“ buvo įdiegtas iš anksto, bet kurie neturi teisės jo naudoti, rodomas dialogo langas, kuriame jie gali pasirinkti išbandyti „Office“, jį įsigyti arba įvesti produkto kodą, kad gautų licenciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2212">Users with pre-installed Office on new machines who have no Office entitlement are shown a dialog through which they can try, buy or enter a product key to get licensed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2213">Šis įvykis užregistruoja vartotojo veiksmą dialogo lange.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2213">This event captures the user action on the dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2214">Šis įvykis naudojamas siekiant stebėti dialogo lange, rodomame vartotojui, kurio įrenginyje „Office“ buvo įdiegtas iš anksto, tačiau kuris neturi teisės jo naudoti, atliekamus veiksmus, ir padeda nustatyti, ar vartotojas gauna licenciją, ar ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2214">This event is used to track the user action taken on the dialog shown to users with no Office entitlement where Office was pre-installed on the machine and helps determining if the user is licensed or unlicensed by design.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2215">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2215">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2216">**Buy** – nurodo, ar vartotojas spustelėjo pirkimo mygtuką, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2216">**Buy** - Tells if the user clicked on the buy button or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2217">**ForceAutoActivate** – nurodo, ar turi būti bandoma suaktyvinti programoje, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2217">**ForceAutoActivate** - Tells if in-app activation should be attempted or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2218">**GoBackToSignIn** – nurodo, ar vartotojas norėjo vėl prisijungti (galimai naudodamas kitą paskyrą)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2218">**GoBackToSignIn** - Tells if the user wanted to sign in again (possibly with another account)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2219">**IsPin** – nurodo, ar vartotojas įvedė PIN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2219">**IsPin** - Tells if the user entered a pin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2220">**ProductKey** – nurodo, ar vartotojas bandė įvesti produkto kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2220">**ProductKey** - Tells if the user tried to enter a product key</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2221">**Try** – nurodo, ar vartotojas spustelėjo išbandymo mygtuką, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2221">**Try** - Tells if the user clicked on the try button or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2222">**UserDismissed** – nurodo, ar vartotojas atmetė dialogo langą ir nepasirinko įsigyti „Office“ arba jo išbandyti; tokiu atveju bus pradėtas atidėjimo laikotarpis arba produktas veiks sumažinto funkcionalumo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2222">**UserDismissed** - This tells if the user dismissed the dialog and thus would be in grace or reduced functionality mode because they didn't choose to buy office or get a trial</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingpurchase"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2223">Office.Licensing.Purchase</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2223">Office.Licensing.Purchase</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2224">*[Šis įvykis buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ komponavimo versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse komponavimo versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2224">*[This event has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2225">Yra eksperimentas, kuris suteikia vartotojui galimybę bandyti ir nustatyti „Office“ automatinį paleidimą tiesiai iš taikomosios programos, nepaliekant taikomosios programos konteksto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2225">We have an experiment that gives the user an option to try and set up autopay for Office directly from an app without ever leaving the context of the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2226">Tai praneša apie sėkmingą to eksperimento įvykdymą arba triktį kartu su klaidos kodu. Tai svarbu nustatant, ar vartotojo būsena yra tinkama ir jam veikia visos funkcijos, taip pat naudojama sistemos sveikatos ir diagnostikos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2226">This reports the success or failure of that experiment along with the error code It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2227">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2227">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2228">**StorePurchaseStatus** – pateikia pirkimo iškvietimo, kuris buvo pateiktas „Windows“ parduotuvėje, klaidos kodą / sėkmingo įvykdymo kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2228">**StorePurchaseStatus** – Represents the error code/success code of the purchase call that was made through windows store</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingsearchforsessiontoken"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2229">Office.Licensing.SearchForSessionToken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2229">Office.Licensing.SearchForSessionToken</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2230">Bendrai naudojamo kompiuterio režimo atveju bandome ieškoti seanso atpažinimo ženklo kompiuteryje. Tai leidžia vartotojui naudoti programą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2230">If the user is running under shared computer activation mode, we try to search for a session token on the machine which allows the user to use the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2231">Šis įvykis praneša apie sėkmingą arba nepavykusį scenarijaus vykdymą kartu su klaidos kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2231">This event reports the success or failure of the scenario along with the error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2232">Tai svarbu nustatant, ar vartotojo būsena yra tinkama ir jam veikia visos funkcijos, taip pat naudojama sistemos sveikatos ir diagnostikos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2232">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2233">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2233">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2234">**LoadLicenseResult** – pateikia klaidos kodą / sėkmingo įvykdymo kodą, susijusį su tuo, ar mums pavyko įkelti dabartinio vartotojo licencijas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2234">**LoadLicenseResult** – Represents the error code/success code of whether we were able to load the licenses for the current user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2235">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – nurodo, ar bandėme atnaujinti vartotojo seanso atpažinimo ženklą oportunistiškai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2235">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – Indicates whether we attempted to renew the user's session token opportunistically</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2236">**SetAcidResult** – pateikia klaidos kodą / sėkmingo įvykdymo kodą, susijusį su tuo, ar mums pavyko nustatyti ACID kaip numatytą reikšmę</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2236">**SetAcidResult** – Represent the error code/success code of whether we were able to set the acid to the expected value</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingshownewdeviceactivationdialog"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2237">Office.Licensing.ShowNewDeviceActivationDialog</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2237">Office.Licensing.ShowNewDeviceActivationDialog</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2238">Pirmąjį kartą įkraunant „Office“ programą bandome parodyti prisijungimo dialogo langą, kuriame iš anksto įvesti atsisiunčiant „Office“ vartotojo naudoti kredencialai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2238">On the first boot of an Office app, we will try to show a sign in dialog pre-populated with the credentials the user employed to download Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2239">Vartotojas gali tęsti prisijungimą naudodamas tuos kredencialus, naudoti kitokius kredencialus arba išjungti dialogo langą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2239">The user can then continue to sign-in with those credentials, use different credentials or dismiss the dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2240">Šis įvykis praneša apie vartotojo atliktą veiksmą, kai jam buvo parodytas šis dialogo langas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2240">This event reports the action taken by the user when presented with this dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2241">Tai svarbu nustatant, ar vartotojo būsena šiuolaikiniame licencijavimo procese yra tinkama, taip pat naudojama sistemos sveikatos ir diagnostikos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2241">It is critical for detecting if a user is in a good state on the modern licensing stack, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2242">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2242">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2243">**UserAction** – vartotojo atlikto veiksmo, kai jam buvo parodytas dialogo langas, identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2243">**UserAction** – Identifier for the action taken by the user when presented with the dialog.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingskutoskuconversion"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2244">Office.Licensing.SkuToSkuConversion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2244">Office.Licensing.SkuToSkuConversion</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2245">Jei licencijuodami vartotoją turime pakeisti vartotojo SKU iš vieno SKU į kitą, išsiunčiame šį signalą kartu su sėkmingo įvykdymo arba trikties kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2245">As part of licensing the user, if we have to change the user's SKU from one SKU to another, we send this signal out along with the success or failure code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2246">Tai svarbu nustatant, ar vartotojo būsena yra tinkama ir jam veikia visos funkcijos, taip pat naudojama sistemos sveikatos ir diagnostikos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2246">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2247">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2247">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2248">**DestinationSku** – SKU, į kurį turi būti konvertuotas šiuo metu įdiegtas produktas, pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2248">**DestinationSku** – Name of the SKU to which the currently installed product should be converted to</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2249">**PendingAcid** – produkto, kurio SKU konvertavimas laukia, ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2249">**PendingAcid** – ID of the product for which a SKU conversion is pending</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2250">**SourceSku** – pradinio SKU, kuris buvo įdiegtas kompiuteryje, pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2250">**SourceSku** – Name of the original SKU that was installed on the machine</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2251">**UninstallProduct** – nurodo, ar senasis produktas bus pašalintas konvertuojant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2251">**UninstallProduct** – Indicates whether the old product will be uninstalled as part of the conversion</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowolsresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2252">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.OLSResults</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2252">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.OLSResults</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2253">Kai vartotojas neturi licencijos, atliekame kelis tarnybų iškvietimus, kad vartotojas gautų licenciją ir suaktyvintų „Office“ produktą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2253">When a user is unlicensed, we make several service calls to get the user into a licensed state and to activate their Office product.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2254">Šis įvykis suaktyvinamas iškvietus „Office“ licencijavimo tarnybą, kad būtų patikrina, ar vartotojas turi teisių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2254">This event gets triggered on calling the Office Licensing Service to check if the user has entitlements.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2255">Šis įvykis bus naudojamas siekiant stebėti vartotojo licencijavimo būseną po „Office“ licencijavimo tarnybos iškvietimo ir „Office“ kliento būseną po bandymo gauti „Office“ suaktyvinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2255">This event is going to be used to track the user licensing health after calling the Office Licensing Service and the Office Client health after attempting to get Office activated.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2256">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2256">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2257">**EntitlementPickerShown** – nurodo, ar vartotojas turėjo kelias teises ir ar jis turėjo pats iš jų pasirinkti, kad gautų licenciją</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2257">**EntitlementPickerShown** - Tells if the user had multiple entitlements and if the user had to manually choose from them to get licensed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2258">**GetAuthResult** – nurodo įvairias galimas kliento būsenas, jei gautas tuščias produkto kodas iš „Office“ licencijavimo tarnybos arba jei vartotojas turi teisę naudotis kitu produktu ir „Office“ turi būti konvertuotas į naująjį produktą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2258">**GetAuthResult** - Tells various states the client might be in like if they got an empty product key from the Office Licensing Service or if they were entitled for another product and Office needs to be converted to the new product</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2259">**GetEntitlementsCount** – nurodo vartotojo turimų teisių skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2259">**GetEntitlementsCount** - Tells the number of entitlements the user has</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2260">**GetEntitlementsSucceeded** – nurodo, ar „Office“ licencijavimo tarnybos API iškvietimas siekiant gauti vartotojo teises buvo sėkmingas, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2260">**GetEntitlementsSucceeded** - Tells if the call to an Office Licensing Service API to retrieve the user's entitlements succeeded or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2261">**GetKeySucceeded** – nurodo, ar „Office“ licencijavimo tarnybos API iškvietimas siekiant gauti kodą buvo sėkmingas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2261">**GetKeySucceeded** - Tells if the call to an Office Licensing Service API to retrieve a key succeeded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2262">**GetNextUserLicenseResult** – nurodo, ar modernus licencijavimo procesas veikė ir ar vartotojas gavo licenciją, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2262">**GetNextUserLicenseResult** - Tells if the modern licensing stack was able to work and if the user got licensed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2263">**InstallKeyResult** – nurodo įvairias priežastis, kodėl vartotojo būsena gali būti netinkama, pvz., jei nepavyko suaktyvinti arba įdiegti kodo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2263">**InstallKeyResult** - Tells various reasons why the user might be in a bad state like if activation failed or the installation of the key failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2264">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** – tai skirta tik informacijai, ar įvykis buvo įtrauktas į telemetrijos tvarkytuvo schemą jo tiesiogiai neužregistruojant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2264">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2265">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileSending** – tai skirta tik informacijai, ar buvo bandoma siųsti įvykį jo prieš tai tiesiogiai neužregistravus telemetrijos tvarkytuvo schemoje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2265">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileSending** - This is just informational and tells if the event was attempted to be sent without explicitly registering for it in the telemetry manager map before hand</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2266">**SentOnDestruction** – tai skirta tik informacijai, ar įvykis buvo įtrauktas į telemetrijos tvarkytuvo schemą ir nebuvo tiesiogiai išsiųstas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2266">**SentOnDestruction** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map and wasn't sent explicitly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2267">**Tag** – naudojama nurodant, iš kurios kodo vietos įvykis buvo išsiųstas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2267">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2268">**VerifyEntitlementsResult** – nurodo įvairias vartotojo būsenas patvirtinus teises, gautas iš „Office“ licencijavimo tarnybos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2268">**VerifyEntitlementsResult** - Tells various states the user might be in after validating the entitlements retrieved from the Office Licensing Service</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowsearchforbindingresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2269">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.SearchForBindingResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2269">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.SearchForBindingResult</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2270">OĮG parduoda įrenginius, kuriuose yra „Office“ (vienų metų prenumerata arba nuolatinė licencija).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2270">OEMs sell machines that come with Office (one-year subscriptions or perpetual).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2271">Už šiuos „Office“ produktus sumokama, kai klientas įsigyja įrenginį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2271">These Office products are paid for when the customer purchases their machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2272">Kompiuteriai, sukonfigūruoti naudojant konkretų registro raktą (OOBEMode: OEMTA), gali turėti „Office“ susiejimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2272">Machines that are set up with a specific regkey (OOBEMode: OEMTA) might have an Office binding associated with it.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2273">Kai paleidžiame „Office“ tokiuose įrenginiuose, atliekame tarnybos patikras, kad sužinotume, ar „Office“ susiejimas atitinka įrenginį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2273">When we boot Office on such machines, we perform service checks to see if an Office binding corresponding to the machine is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2274">Telemetrijos veikla stebi sėkmės ir nesėkmės taškus ieškant susiejimo. Taip siekiame užtikrinti, kad įrenginiai, kurie turi susiejimą, galėtų sėkmingai jį iškviesti ir kad mūsų paslaugos būtų geros būsenos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2274">This telemetry activity tracks the success and failure points in searching for a binding so that we can ensure that machines that do have a binding can successfully fetch them, and that our services are healthy.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2275">Ši veikla nestebi įrenginių, kurie, kaip nustatoma atlikus tarnybos patikras, neturi susiejimų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2275">This activity does not track machines that turn out to not have any bindings associated with them after we check with our services.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2276">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2276">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2277">**DexShouldRetry** – signalas, kad įvyko bandymo iš naujo problema (nėra interneto arba neveikia serveriai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2277">**DexShouldRetry** - Signal that we’ve hit a retryable issue (no internet or servers are down)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2278">**GenuineTicketFailure** – nurodo trikties HRESULT, kai bandoma gauti įrenginio „Windows“ autentišką leidimą / produkto kodą (WPK).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2278">**GenuineTicketFailure** - Tells us the failure HRESULT when trying to get the machine's Windows genuine ticket/product key (WPK).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2279">**PinValidationFailure** – nurodo, kodėl nepavyko PIN patvirtinimo procesas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2279">**PinValidationFailure** - Tells us why the pin validation process failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2280">Galimos klaidos:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2280">Possible errors:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2281">GeoBlocked</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2281">GeoBlocked</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2282">InvalidFormat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2282">InvalidFormat</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2283">InvalidPin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2283">InvalidPin</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2284">InvalidState</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2284">InvalidState</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2285">InvalidVersion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2285">InvalidVersion</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2286">Unknown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2286">Unknown</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2287">Used</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2287">Used</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2288">**PinValidationResult** – nurodo PIN, kurio nepavyko atpažinti, patvirtinimo rezultatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2288">**PinValidationResult** - Tells us the pin validation result of a pin that we failed to crack.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2289">**Pkpn** – PKPN diapazonas, kuriam priklauso PIN.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2289">**Pkpn** - The pkpn range that the pin belongs to.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2290">**Success** – nurodo, kad sėkmingai iškvietėme galiojantį įrenginio „Office“ susiejimą (PIN).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2290">**Success** - Indicates that we successfully fetched a valid Office binding (pin) for the machine.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2291">**Tag** – nurodo, kuriame etape nustojome ieškoti susiejimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2291">**Tag** - Tells us at which step we stopped searching for a binding.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2292">Galimos žymės:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2292">Possible tags:</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2293">0x03113809    Nėra interneto / tarnybos klaida patvirtinant PIN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2293">0x03113809    No internet/service error while validating pin</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2294">0x0311380a    PIN patvirtinimo klaida, išsiųsta su lauko PinValidationFailure reikšme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2294">0x0311380a    Pin validation failure, sent with PinValidationFailure field</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2295">0x0310410f    Būsena Pavyko, išsiųsta su lauko Success reikšme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2295">0x0310410f    Success, sent with Success field</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2296">0x0311380d    Klaidos, kurias galima bandyti išspręsti pakartotinai (interneto problemos, nežinomos klaidos)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2296">0x0311380d    Retry-able errors (internet issues, unknown errors)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2297">0x0311380e    Klaidos, kurių negalima bandyti išspręsti pakartotinai (baigėsi susiejimo pasiūlymo laikas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2297">0x0311380e    Non-retry-able errors (binding offer expired)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2298">0x0311380f    Kitos klaidos (nepavyko licencijuoti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2298">0x0311380f    Other errors (unable to license)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2299">0x03104111    Nepavyko atpažinti „Office“ PIN; siunčiama su lauko PinValidationResult reikšme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2299">0x03104111    Failed to crack the Office pin, sent with PinValidationResult field</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2300">**WpkBindingFailure** – nurodo „Office“ PIN, skirto įrenginio WPK, gavimo klaidos kodą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2300">**WpkBindingFailure** - Tells us the error code of getting the Office pin bound to the machine's WPK.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowshowafodialogs"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2301">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowAFODialogs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2301">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowAFODialogs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2302">Sėkmingai gavus galiojantį „Office“ PIN, skirtą įrenginiui, kuriame iš anksto įdiegtas „Office“, parodome vartotojui prisijungimo arba panaudojimo dialogo langą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2302">After successfully obtaining a valid Office pin bound to a machine pre-bundled with Office, we show the user either a sign-in dialog or a redemption dialog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2303">Kai PIN panaudojamas, parodome GVLS dialogo langą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2303">Once the pin is redeemed, we show the EULA dialog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2304">Modernizuodami AFO funkciją atnaujinome du dialogo langus, kad suteiktume daugiau informacijos apie įrenginyje esantį „Office“ produktą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2304">As a part of our modernizing AFO feature, we refreshed the two dialogs to convey more information regarding the Office product that comes with the machine.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2305">Ši telemetrija skirta stebėti, ar naudojant funkciją vartotojams kyla mažiau nesklandumų gaunant produktą. Stebima panaudojimo proceso eiga ir išėjimo taškai (kuris dialogo langas buvo atmestas).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2305">This telemetry is to track if our feature successfully reduces user friction in redeeming their product by tracking the flow and exit points of the redemption process (which dialog was dismissed).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2306">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2306">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2307">**ActionActivate** – signalas, kad vartotojas spustelėjo mygtuką „Aktyvinti“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2307">**ActionActivate** - Signal that user clicked the “Activate” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2308">**ActionChangeAccount** – signalas, kad vartotojas spustelėjo hipersaitą „Naudoti kitą paskyrą“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2308">**ActionChangeAccount** -  Signal that user clicked the “Use a different account” hyperlink.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2309">**ActionCreateAccount** – signalas, kad vartotojas spustelėjo mygtuką „Kurti paskyrą“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2309">**ActionCreateAccount** - Signal that user clicked the “Create account” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2310">**ActionSignIn** – signalas, kad vartotojas spustelėjo mygtuką „Prisijungti“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2310">**ActionSignIn** - Signal that user clicked the “Sign in” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2311">**CurrentView** – vartotojo uždaryto dialogo lango tipas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2311">**CurrentView** - The type of dialog the user closed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2312">**DialogEULA** – signalas, kad parodėme „Patvirtinti EULA“ dialogo langą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2312">**DialogEULA** -  Signal that we showed the ‘Accept EULA’ dialog.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2313">**DialogRedemption** – signalas, kad parodėme AFO padengimo dialogo langą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2313">**DialogRedemption** - Signal that we showed the AFO redemption dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2314">**DialogSignIn** – signalas, kad parodėme AFO prisijungimo dialogo langą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2314">**DialogSignIn** - Signal that we showed the AFO sign-in dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2315">**EmptyRedemptionDefaults** – signalas, kad nepavyko gauti numatytosios padengimo informacijos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2315">**EmptyRedemptionDefaults** - Signal that we failed to fetch default redemption information.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2316">**GetRedemptionInfo** – signalas, kad bandome gauti demografinę informaciją apie PIN padengimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2316">**GetRedemptionInfo** - Signal that we’re fetching demographic information for pin redemption.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2317">**MalformedCountryCode** – signalas, kad šalies kodas, būtinas PIN padengimui, yra netinkamai suformuotas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2317">**MalformedCountryCode** - Signal that the country code needed for pin redemption is malformed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2318">**OExDetails** – klaidos informacija, kurią gauname, kai atmetamas prisijungimo dialogo langas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2318">**OExDetails** - The error details we get back when identity's sign-in dialog was dismissed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2319">**OExType** – klaidos tipas, kurį gauname, kai atmetamas prisijungimo dialogo langas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2319">**OExType** - The error type we get back when identity's sign-in dialog was dismissed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2320">**Tag** – nurodo, kuriame etape vartotojas išėjo iš AFO panaudojimo proceso.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2320">**Tag** - Tells us at which step the user exits the AFO redemption process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2321">Galimos žymės:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2321">Possible tags:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2322">0x0311380b    Vartotojas atmetė prisijungimo dialogo langą panaudojimo dialogo lange</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2322">0x0311380b    User dismissed identity's sign-in dialog from redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2323">0x0311380c    Nepavyko automatiškai įkelti tapatybės, kai vartotojas prisijungė panaudojimo dialogo lange</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2323">0x0311380c    Failed to auto-load an identity post user sign-in from redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2324">0x03113810    Nepavyko įkelti paskyros demografinės informacijos (šalies kodo, kalbos, valiutos, bandomojo pasiūlymo ir rinkodaros nuostatų)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2324">0x03113810    Failed to load the account's demographic information (country code, language,     currency, trial offer, and marketing preferences)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2325">0x03113805    Vartotojas atmetė prisijungimo dialogo langą prisijungimo dialogo lange</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2325">0x03113805    User dismissed identity's sign-in dialog from sign-in dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2326">0x03113806 Nepavyko automatiškai įkelti tapatybės, kai vartotojas prisijungė prisijungimo dialogo lange</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2326">0x03113806    Failed to auto-load an identity post user sign-in from sign-in dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2327">0x03113807 Nepavyko automatiškai įkelti tapatybės</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2327">0x03113807    Failed to auto-load an identity</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2328">0x03113811 Vartotojas uždarė prisijungimo / panaudojimo dialogo langą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2328">0x03113811    User closed the sign-in/redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2329">0x03113812 Vartotojas uždarė sutikimo su GVLS dialogo langą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2329">0x03113812    User closed the accept EULA dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2330">0x03113808 Vartotojas sutiko su GVLS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2330">0x03113808    User accepted the EULA</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2331">0x03113811 Vartotojas uždarė dialogo langą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2331">0x03113811      User closed a dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2332">0x2370e3a0 Vartotojas uždarė dialogo langą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2332">0x2370e3a0      User closed a dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2333">0x2370e3c1 Eiti į žiniatinklį siekiant padengti PIN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2333">0x2370e3c1      Go to web for pin redemption</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2334">0x2370e3a1 Eiti į žiniatinklį siekiant padengti PIN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2334">0x2370e3a1      Go to web for pin redemption</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2335">0x2370e3c0 Dialogo lango sekos ciklas dėl vartotojo grįžimo ir perėjimo į priekį dialogo langų sraute</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2335">0x2370e3c0      Dialog sequence looped caused by user going back and forth in the dialog flow</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2336">0x2370e3a3 Vartotojas spustelėjo hipersaitą „Ne dabar“, todėl buvo praleistas AFO pasiūlymas tame seanse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2336">0x2370e3a3      User clicked “Not now” hyperlink which skips the AFO offer for that session</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2337">0x2370e3a2 Vartotojas spustelėjo hipersaitą „Niekada šito man nerodyti“, todėl buvo išjungtas AFO pasiūlymas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2337">0x2370e3a2      User clicked on “Never show this to me” hyperlink which disables the AFO offer</span></span>


- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2338">**UseInAppRedemption** – nurodo, ar vartotojai išlaikomi programoje ir gali panaudoti PIN joje, ar siunčiami į žiniatinklį, kad panaudotų iškviestą PIN (iš anksto įvestą).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2338">**UseInAppRedemption** - Tells us if we're keeping users in-app for redemption or sending them to the web to redeem their fetched pin (pre-populated).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2339">**UseModernAFO** – nurodo, ar naudojame naująją, ar senąją AFO funkciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2339">**UseModernAFO** - Tells us if we're using the new or old AFO experience.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowshowtrybuydialogforoobe"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2340">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowTryBuyDialogForOOBE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2340">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowTryBuyDialogForOOBE</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2341">Kai naujuose įrenginiuose yra iš anksto įdiegtas „Office“ ir vartotojas neturi teisės jo naudoti, parodome dialogo langą, kuris suteikia vartotojui galimybę išbandyti „Office“, jį įsigyti arba įvesti produkto kodą, kad galėtų gauti licenciją. Šis įvykis stebi, ar dialogo langas buvo parodytas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2341">When new machines have Office pre-installed and the user doesn't have an entitlement we show a dialog which gives the user the option to try, buy or enter a product key so that the user can get licensed and this event tracks if the dialog was shown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2342">Šis įvykis padės sužinoti, ar vartotojui buvo parodytas dialogo langas su parinktimis išbandyti, įsigyti produktą arba įvesti produkto kodą; tai mums padės nustatyti, ar vartotojas turėjo galimybę gauti licenciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2342">This event will help with knowing if the dialog was shown to the user to try, buy or enter the product key and hence will help us determine if the user had the opportunity to get licensed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2343">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2343">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2344">**ActiveView** – nurodo vartotojui parodyto dialogo lango ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2344">**ActiveView** - Tells the dialog ID shown to the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2345">**CurrentOOBEMode** – nurodo išankstinio diegimo režimą (OOBE režimą, pvz., AFO, OĮG ir pan.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2345">**CurrentOOBEMode** - Tells the pre-install mode (OOBE mode such as AFO, OEM etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2346">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** – tai skirta tik informacijai, ar įvykis buvo įtrauktas į telemetrijos tvarkytuvo schemą jo tiesiogiai neužregistruojant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2346">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2347">**SentOnDestruction** – tai skirta tik informacijai, ar įvykis buvo įtrauktas į telemetrijos tvarkytuvo schemą ir nebuvo tiesiogiai išsiųstas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2347">**SentOnDestruction** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map and wasn't sent explicitly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2348">**ShowTryButton** – nurodo, ar vartotojui dialogo lange buvo rodomas išbandymo mygtukas, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2348">**ShowTryButton** - Tells if the Try Button was shown to the user on the dialog or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2349">**Tag** – naudojama nurodant, iš kurios kodo vietos įvykis buvo išsiųstas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2349">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowtrialflow"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2350">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.TrialFlow</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2350">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.TrialFlow</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2351">Kai licencijos neturintis vartotojas, kurio įrenginyje iš anksto įdiegtas „Office“, bando gauti bandomąją versiją, suaktyvinamas šis įvykis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2351">When an unlicensed user of Office pre-installed on a machine is attempting to get a trial, this event gets triggered.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2352">Jis naudojamas siekiant sužinoti, kokį kelią vartotojas pasirinko, kad gautų bandomąją versiją, ir ar buvo kokių nors klaidų gaunant bandomąją versiją pirkimo programoje srityje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2352">It is used to see which path the user would follow to get a trial and if there were any errors while getting the trial through in-app purchases.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2353">Atsižvelgiant į vartotojo veiksmą ir rezultatą pirkimo programoje srityje, vartotojas gali negauti licencijos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2353">Depending on the user action and the result of the in-app purchase the user could end up being unlicensed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2354">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2354">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2355">**HasConnectivity** – nurodo, ar vartotojas turi interneto ryšį. Jei ryšio nėra, vartotojas gali naudoti atidėjimo licenciją penkias dienas arba produktas gali veikti sumažinto funkcionalumo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2355">**HasConnectivity** - Tells if the user has internet connectivity and in case there isn't the user might have to use a grace license for five days or may be in reduced functionality mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2356">**InAppTrialPurchase** – nurodo, ar įgalintas variantas paleidžiant „Store“ pirkimo SDK, kad būtų užfiksuoti PI ir įsigyta bandomoji versija programoje *[Šis laukas pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ komponavimo versijų, tačiau vis dar gali būti rodomas senesnėse komponavimo versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2356">**InAppTrialPurchase** - Tells if the flight is enabled for launching the Store Purchase SDK to capture PI and purchase a trial from within the application *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2357">**IsRS1OrGreater** – nurodo, ar OS versija yra naujesnė nei RS1, ar ne, nes „Store“ pirkimo SDK turi būti naudojamas, tik jei OS versija yra naujesnė nei RS1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2357">**IsRS1OrGreater** - Tells if the OS Version is greater than RS1 or not since the Store Purchase SDK should be used only if the OS Version is greater that RS1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2358">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding**: tai skirta tik informacijai, ar įvykis buvo įtrauktas į telemetrijos tvarkytuvo schemą jo tiesiogiai neužregistruojant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2358">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding**: This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2359">**OEMSendToWebForTrial** – nurodo, ar variantas yra įgalintas, kad vartotojai būtų siunčiami į žiniatinklį gauti bandomajai versijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2359">**OEMSendToWebForTrial** - Tells if the flight is enabled to send users to the web to redeem a trial</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2360">**StoreErrorConditions** – nurodo įvairias sąlygas, kuriomis galėjo nepavykti atlikti SDK pirkimo parduotuvėje *[Šis laukas pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ komponavimo versijų, tačiau vis dar gali būti rodomas senesnėse komponavimo versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2360">**StoreErrorConditions** - Tells the various conditions under which the Store Purchase SDK could have failed *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2361">**StoreErrorHResult** – nurodo klaidos kodą, pateiktą atliekant SDK pirkimą parduotuvėje *[Šis laukas pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ komponavimo versijų, tačiau vis dar gali būti rodomas senesnėse komponavimo versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2361">**StoreErrorHResult** - Tells the error code returned from the Store Purchase SDK *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2362">**StorePurchaseStatusResult** – nurodo „Store“ pirkimo SDK iškvietimo rezultatą ir ar vartotojas įsigijo, ar ne. Tai padės nustatyti, ar vartotojas turi gauti licenciją naudoti „Office“*[Šis laukas pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ komponavimo versijų, tačiau vis dar gali būti rodomas senesnėse komponavimo versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2362">**StorePurchaseStatusResult** - Tells the result of calling the Store Purchase SDK and if the user made a purchase or not which will help determine if the user should get licensed to use Office *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2363">**Tag** – naudojama nurodant, iš kurios kodo vietos įvykis buvo išsiųstas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2363">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2364">**UserSignedInExplicitly** – nurodo, ar vartotojas prisijungė tiesiogiai, tokiu atveju nukreiptume vartotojus į bandomosios versijos svetainę *[Šis laukas pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ komponavimo versijų, tačiau vis dar gali būti rodomas senesnėse komponavimo versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2364">**UserSignedInExplicitly** - Tells if the user signed in explicitly in which case, we would re-direct users to the web for the trial *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingusegracekey"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2365">Office.Licensing.UseGraceKey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2365">Office.Licensing.UseGraceKey</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2366">Jei dėl kokios nors priežasties nepavyksta licencijuoti vartotojo, įdiegiame atidėjimo raktą ir išsiunčiame šį signalą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2366">For some reason if we are unable to license the user, we install a grace key and send out this signal that signifies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2367">Tai svarbu nustatant, ar vartotojo būsena yra tinkama ir jam veikia visos funkcijos, taip pat naudojama sistemos sveikatos ir diagnostikos tikslais, jei vartotojas praneša apie kompiuterio problemą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2367">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2368">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2368">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2369">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – nurodo, ar bandėme oportunistiškai atnaujinti vartotojui bendrai naudojamo kompiuterio aktyvinimo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2369">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – Indicates if we attempted an opportunistic renewal for the user in shared computer activation mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2370">**ReArmResult** – nurodo įdiegto rakto, kuris gali pratęsti dabartinės licencijos galiojimą, pradinės licencijavimo būsenos atkūrimo rezultatą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2370">**ReArmResult** – Indicates the result of rearming the installed key which can extend the expiry of the current license</span></span>

### <a name="onenoteenrollmentresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2371">OneNote.EnrollmentResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2371">OneNote.EnrollmentResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2372">Šis įvykis užregistruoja būseną po „Intune“ registracijos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2372">This event logs the status upon Intune enrollment.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2373">Šis scenarijus būdingas paskyroms, kuriose įgalinta „Intune“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2373">This scenario is specific to Intune enabled accounts.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2374">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2374">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2375">**EnrollmentResult** – „Intune“ registracijos rezultatas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2375">**EnrollmentResult** - The result of Intune enrollment</span></span>

### <a name="skuproductpricenullevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2376">SKU.PRODUCT.PRICE.NULL.EVENT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2376">SKU.PRODUCT.PRICE.NULL.EVENT</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2377">Šis įvykis naudojamas įvykiams užfiksuoti, siekiant įvertinti klaidos poveikį, dėl kurio vartotojai šiandien SKU parinkiklio ekrane vietoj kainos mato „Null“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2377">This event is used to capture events to quantify the impact of the bug due to which users today see “Null” instead of a price at the SKU chooser screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2378">Klaida bus diagnozuota toliau, siekiant nustatyti gedimo šalinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2378">The bug will be diagnosed further to determine a fix.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2379">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2379">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2380">**PriceNotFound** – Kainos nerandamos iš parduotuvės.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2380">**PriceNotFound** - Prices is not found from the store.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2381">**StoreNotInitilized** – Kai parduotuvė nėra sėkmingai inicijuota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2381">**StoreNotInitilized** - When store is not initialized successfully.</span></span>


## <a name="microsoft-autoupdate-mau-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2382">„Microsoft AutoUpdate“ (MAU) įvykiai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2382">Microsoft AutoUpdate (MAU) events</span></span>

### <a name="additionalappinfoinvalidpreference"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2383">additionalappinfo_invalidpreference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2383">additionalappinfo.invalidpreference</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2384">Šis įvykis praneša apie neleistiną nuostatų rinkinį, rodantį daugiau informacijos, susijusios su produkto tarnybos pabaiga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2384">This event reports on invalid preference set to display more information with respect to End of Service for a product.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2385">Naudojame šią informaciją, kad patartume klientams nustatyti tinkamas nuostatas, kad matytumėte papildomą informaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2385">We use this information to advise customers to set correct preferences in order to see additional information.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2386">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2386">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2387">**App** – programos siuntimo procesas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2387">**App** – The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2388">**AppInfo_Language** – kalba, kuria veikia programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2388">**AppInfo_Language** – The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2389">**AppVersionLong** – programos versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2389">**AppVersionLong** – The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2390">**Channel** – auditorijos nuostatos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2390">**Channel** – The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2391">**Device_NetworkCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2391">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2392">**DeviceID**– įrenginio identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2392">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2393">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2393">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2394">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2394">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2395">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2395">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2396">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2396">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2397">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2397">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2398">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2398">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2399">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2399">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2400">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** – pirmieji trys IP adreso aštuonkeliai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2400">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first three octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2401">**Reason** – informacija apie netinkamą įrašą nuostatose</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2401">**Reason** - Details on the invalid entry in preferences</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2402">**SessionId** – seanso identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2402">**SessionId** - The identifier for the session</span></span>

### <a name="appdelegatelaunch"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2403">appdelegate_launch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2403">appdelegate.launch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2413">**DeviceID**– įrenginio identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2413">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2414">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2414">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2415">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2415">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2416">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2416">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2417">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2417">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2418">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2418">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2419">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2419">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2420">**HowTocheck** – naujinimų tikrinimo pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2420">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2421">**Payload** – statinio teksto, nurodančios paleisties būseną, rinkinys.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2421">**Payload** - A set of static text indicating launch status.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2422">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2422">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

### <a name="appregistryinfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2532">appregistry.info</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2532">appregistry.info</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2533">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad programa paleista.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2533">This event denotes that the application launched.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2534">Naudojame šį įvykį, kad pateiktumėte taikomųjų programų, kurioms MAU gali valdyti naujinimus, kopijų skaičių, taip pat jų versiją ir diegimo vietą (numatytoji ar kita).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2534">We use this event to list the applications for which MAU can control updates, the number of copies available as well as their version and install location (default or other).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2549">**Payload** – pateikia informaciją apie identifikatorių sąrašą, kurį taikomoji programa naudoja registruodamasi „Microsoft AutoUpdate“ paslaugoms, ir registruotų taikomosios programos diegimų skaičių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2549">**Payload** - Contains information on list of identifiers application uses to register with Microsoft Autoupdate services and number of installations registered for the application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2584">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2584">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2589">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2589">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-2744">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-2744">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4490">**Device_NetworkCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4490">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4492">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4492">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4493">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4493">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4494">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4494">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4497">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4497">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4498">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4498">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4505">**Success** – Bulio logikos eilutė, nurodanti, ar buvo sėkmingai paleistas MAU demono procesas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4505">**Success** – The string Boolean indicating whether MAU daemon process was successfully launched.</span></span>


### <a name="fbamausilentupdate"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4506">fba.mausilentupdate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4506">fba.mausilentupdate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4515">**DeviceID**– įrenginio identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4515">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4516">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4516">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4518">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4518">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4520">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4520">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4521">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4521">**EventInfo_Time** -   The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4522">**HowToCheck** – kaip tikrinti parametrus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4522">**HowToCheck** - How to check setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4523">**Payload** – statinis tekstas *[Šis laukas buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ komponavimo versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse komponavimo versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4523">**Payload** - Static text *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4529">Šis įvykis praneša informaciją apie registruotą taikomąją programą, kuri nukreipiama per „Microsoft“ automatinius naujinimus (MAU).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4529">This event reports on information that a registered application is routing through Microsoft Auto Update (MAU).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4530">Pvz., galutinių tarnybų pranešimai išstumiami per MAU pranešimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4530">For example, end-of-service messages are pushed through MAU notification.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4531">Šis įvykis naudojamas nustatyti įrenginių, kurie rodo šį konkretų pranešimą, kiekį, kad būtų galima nustatyti informacijos sklaidos sėkmę.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4531">We use this event to determine the volume of devices that are displaying this particular notification, to determine the success of information dissemination.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4535">**AppInfo_Language** – kalba, kuria veikia taikomoji programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4535">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4536">**AppVersionLong** – taikomosios programos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4536">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4537">**Channel** – auditorijos pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4537">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4538">**Device_NetworkCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4538">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4539">**DeviceID**– įrenginio identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4539">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4540">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4540">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4541">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4541">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4542">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4542">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4543">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4543">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4544">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4544">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4545">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4545">**EventInfo_Time** -  The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4546">**HowToCheck** – kaip tikrinti parametrus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4546">**HowToCheck** - How to check setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4547">**NotificationEvent** – statinis tekstas, nurodantis, kokio tipo pranešimas taikomas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4547">**NotificationEvent** - Static text indicating what type of notification is being applied.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4548">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4548">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

### <a name="fbamultipledaemon"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4551">fba.multipledaemon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4551">fba.multipledaemon</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4552">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad aptiktas kitas „Microsoft Update“ pagalbinės priemonės egzempliorius ir dabartinis egzempliorius bus nutrauktas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4552">This event indicates that another instance of Microsoft Update Assistant has been detected and current instance will be terminated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4553">Naudosime šį įvykį, kad nustatytumėte įrenginių, kurie bando vykdyti kelis naujinimo pagalbinės priemonės egzempliorius, kiekį ir, jei reikia, sukurti sprendimo būdą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4553">We will be using this event to determine volume of devices that attempt to run multiple instances of Update Assistant and design a workaround if need arises.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4554">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4554">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

### <a name="fbasilentupdateappterminationeventreceived"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4850">fbasilentupdate.appterminationeventreceived</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4850">fbasilentupdate.appterminationeventreceived</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4851">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Microsoft AutoUpdate“ gavo „Apple“ įvykį, informuojantį apie taikomosios programos nutraukimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4851">This event indicates Microsoft Autoupdate has received an Apple event informing the application has been terminated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4852">Šis įvykis naudojamas, kad būtų užtikrinta, jog naujinimo procesas veikia taip, kaip tikėtasi, ir padėti pašalinti klaidas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4852">We use this event for ensuring the update process works as expected and to help troubleshoot errors.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4856">**AppInfo_Language** – kalba, kuria veikia taikomoji programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4856">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4857">**AppVersionLong** – taikomosios programos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4857">**AppVersionLong** - The application Version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4858">**Channel** – auditorijos pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4858">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4859">**Device_NetworkCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4859">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4860">**DeviceID**– įrenginio identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4860">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4861">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4861">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4862">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4862">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4863">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4863">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4865">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4865">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4866">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4866">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4867">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4867">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4868">**HowTocheck** – naujinimų tikrinimo pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4868">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4869">**Payload** – turi identifikatorių, kuris naudojamas sekti naujinimo veiklą ir taikomosios programos paketo ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4869">**Payload** - Contains an identifier used to track an update activity and application bundle ID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4870">Taip pat gali turėti klaidos eilutę, jei „Microsoft AutoUpdate“ nustato, kad taikomoji programa vis dar veikia, nors nutraukimo įvykis buvo gautas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4870">This may also contain an error string if Microsoft Autoupdate determines the application is still running even though termination event was received.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4871">*[Šis laukas buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ komponavimo versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse komponavimo versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4871">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4873">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** – pirmieji 3 IP adreso aštuonkeliai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4873">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4874">**SessionId** – seanso identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4874">**SessionId** - The identifier for the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4875">**UpdateID** – taikomosios programos naujinimo identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4875">**UpdateID** – The identifier of the application update.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-4892">**HowTocheck** – naujinimų tikrinimo pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-4892">**HowTocheck** – The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5548">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5548">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5549">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5549">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>
