### <a name="installedappacknowledgedcoreappleevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5764">installedapp.acknowledgedcoreappleevent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5764">installedapp.acknowledgedcoreappleevent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5765">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Microsoft“ automatinis naujinimas (MAU) iš registruotos programos gavo „Apple“ įvykio patvirtinimą, kad nutrauktų programą ir tęstų laukiantį programos naujinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5765">This event indicates Microsoft Auto Update (MAU) has received an Apple event acknowledgment from a registered application to terminate the application to proceed with pending application update.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5766">Šis įvykis naudojamas siekiant padėti plėtoti būsimą patobulinimą ir sumažinti vartotojų trukdžių naujinant programą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5766">This event is used to help develop future enhancement to minimize user interruption during application updates.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5767">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5767">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5768">**App** – taikomosios programos siuntimo procesas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5768">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5769">**AppID** – atnaujinamos taikomosios programos identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5769">**AppID** - Identifier for the application being updated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5770">**AppInfo_Language** – kalba, kuria veikia programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5770">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5771">**AppleEventClass** – nurodo, kokio tipo įvykis siunčiamas/pripažįstamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5771">**AppleEventClass** - Indicates type of event being sent/acknowledged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5772">**AppleEventID** – unikalus siuntimo/pripažinto įvykio identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5772">**AppleEventID** - Unique identifier for the event being sent/acknowledged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5773">**AppVersionLong** – taikomosios programos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5773">**AppVersionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5774">**Channel** – auditorijos pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5774">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5775">**Device_NetworkCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5775">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5776">**DeviceID**– įrenginio identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5776">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5777">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5777">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5778">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5778">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5779">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5779">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5780">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5780">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5781">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5781">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5782">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5782">**EventInfo_Time** -   The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5783">**HowToCheck** – kaip tikrinti parametrus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5783">**HowToCheck** - How to check setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5784">**Payload** – turi bandymų iš naujo skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5784">**Payload** - Contains retry count</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5786">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** – pirmieji 3 IP adreso aštuonkeliai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5786">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5879">**AppID** – atnaujinamos taikomosios programos identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5879">**AppID** - Identifier for the application being updated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5880">**AppInfo_Language** – kalba, kuria veikia programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5880">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5881">**AppleEventClass** – nurodo, kokio tipo įvykis siunčiamas/pripažįstamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5881">**AppleEventClass** - Indicates type of event being sent/acknowledged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5882">**AppleEventID** – unikalus siuntimo/pripažinto įvykio identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5882">**AppleEventID** - Unique identifier for the event being sent/acknowledged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5888">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5888">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, wired, unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5889">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5889">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the operating system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5890">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5890">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5891">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5891">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5892">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5892">**EventInfo_Time** -   The time at which the logged event took place</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-5936">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-5936">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6319">Šis įvykis reguliariai praneša apie „MicrosoftAutoUpdate“ proceso būseną.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6319">This event reports on status of MicrosoftAutoUpdate process periodically.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6320">Konkrečiai, jis praneša apie tai, kokios likusios užduotys laukia atnaujinimo pagalbinės priemonės, ir vartotojo sąsajos ataskaitose nurodoma, ar procesas baigiamas dėl vartotojo neveikimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6320">Specifically, it reports on what remaining tasks process is waiting on for completion for Update Assistant, and in the case of UI it reports on whether process is terminating due to user inaction.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6321">Šį įvykį naudojame norėdami nustatyti, kas neleidžia atnaujinimo pagalbinei priemonei baigti naujinimų ir nutraukimo ir ar vartotojo sąsajos nutraukiamos dėl vartotojo neveikimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6321">We use this event to determine what is preventing Update Assistant from completing updates and terminating and, whether the UI is terminating due to user inaction.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6322">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6322">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6323">**App** – taikomosios programos siuntimo procesas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6323">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6324">**AppInfo_Language** – kalba, kuria veikia taikomoji programa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6324">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6325">**AppVersionLong** – taikomosios programos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6325">**AppVersionLong** - The application Version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6326">**Channel** – auditorijos pirmenybė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6326">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6327">**dataCollectionDialog** – Bulio logika nurodo, ar procesas laukia vartotojo atsakymo duomenų rinkimo dialogo lange</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6327">**dataCollectionDialog** - Boolean indicating whether the process is waiting for user response on Data Collection Dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6328">**Device_NetworkCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6328">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6329">**DeviceID**– įrenginio identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6329">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6330">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6330">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6331">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – tinklo tipas (Wi-Fi, laidinis, nežinomas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6331">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6332">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – operacinės sistemos komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6332">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6333">**Event_ReceivedTime** – laikas, kuriuo buvo gauta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6333">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6334">**EventInfo_Name** – užregistruoto telemetrijos įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6334">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6335">**EventInfo_Time** – laikas, kada įvyko užregistruotasis įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6335">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6336">**forcedUpdateDialog** – Bulio logika nurodo, ar procesas laukia vartotojo atsakymo priverstinio naujinimo dialogo lange</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6336">**forcedUpdateDialog** - Boolean indicating whether the process is waiting for user response on Forced Update Dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6337">**HowToCheck** – kaip tikrinti parametrus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6337">**HowToCheck** - How To Check setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6338">**isBusy** – Bulio logika nurodo, ar procesas užimtas naudojant aktyvų naujinimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6338">**isBusy** - Boolean indicating whether the process is busy with active update</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6339">**Isneaktyvus** – Bulio logika nurodo, ar procesas ilgą laiką laukė vartotojo veiksmų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6339">**isInactive** - Boolean indicating whether the process has been waiting for user action for prolonged period of time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6340">**isWaiting** – Bulio logika nurodo, ar procesas laukia vartotojo atsakymo dėl pranešimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6340">**isWaiting** - Boolean indicating whether the process is waiting for user response on notification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6341">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – įrenginio šalis (pagrįsta IP adresu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6341">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6342">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** – pirmieji 3 IP adreso aštuonkeliai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6342">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6343">**SessionId** – seanso identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6343">**SessionId** - The identifier for the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-6344">**SessionLength** – dabartinio proceso seanso trukmė sekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-6344">**SessionLength** - Length of current process session in seconds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8261">**DeviceInfo_Model** – įrenginio aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8261">**DeviceInfo_Model** -The hardware model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8282">**Gosid** – visuotinio objekto srities ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8282">**Gosid** – global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8288">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – nurodo, ar bloknoto lygio sinchronizavimo klaida suglaudinta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8288">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8289">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – nurodo, ar bloknoto lygio sinchronizavimo klaida netikėta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8289">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8290">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – nurodo, ar sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaida suglaudinta, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8290">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8292">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – nurodo, ar bloknotas sinchronizuotas naudojant šiuolaikinį puslapio turinio sinchronizavimą, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8292">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8293">**LastAttemptedSync** – laiko žyma, nurodanti, kada bloknotas buvo bandytas sinchronizuoti paskutinį kartą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8293">**LastAttemptedSync** – timestamp when the notebook was attempted to be synced last time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8297">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** – nurodo, ar sinchronizavimą reikia paleisti iš naujo dėl nesuderinamumų, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8297">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** – does the sync need to restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8298">**NotebookErrorCode** – nurodo, kad bloknoto lygio sinchronizavimo klaidos kodas įrašytas bloknoto diagramos srityje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8298">**NotebookErrorCode** – notebook level sync error code saved on notebook graph space</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8299">**NotebookId** – bloknoto ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8299">**NotebookId** – notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8300">**NotebookType** – bloknoto tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8300">**NotebookType** – notebook type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8301">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** – nurodo, ar sinchronizavimas paleidžiamas iš naujo dėl nesuderinamumų, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8301">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** – does the sync restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8302">**SectionError_Code** – skaitinis arba raidinis kodas, naudojamas nustatyti sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaidos pobūdį ir (arba) kodėl ji įvyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8302">**SectionError_Code** – a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the section sync error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8303">**SectionError_Description** – sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaidos aprašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8303">**SectionError_Description** – a description of the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8304">**SectionError_Tag** – nurodo, kur kode įvyksta sekcijos sinchronizavimo klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8304">**SectionError_Tag** – indicate where in the code throws the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8307">**SyncDestinationType** – nurodo sinchronizacijos paskirties tipą, pvz., „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint Online“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8307">**SyncDestinationType** – sync destination type, i.e. OneDrive or SharePoint Online</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragerealtimewebsocketsessioninfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8314">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8314">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8315">Šis įvykis registruoja „WebSocket“ sinchronizavimo rezultatus, kad OneNot" moderniame puslapyje turinys būtų sinchronizuojamas šiuolaikiška hierarchija. Jis naudojamas norint suprasti, kiek yra unikalių sinchronizavimo tikslų, apskaičiuojant „OneNote“ sinchronizavimo balą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8315">This event logs WebSocket sync result for both OneNote modern page content sync modern hierarchy sync. It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8316">Jis taip pat naudojamas „OneNote“ modernių sinchronizavimo efektyvumo ataskaitų srityje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8316">It is also used for OneNote modern sync performance dashboard.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8317">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8317">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8318">**CloseReason** – „Web Socket“ uždarymo priežastis, pvz., nenormalus uždarymas ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8318">**CloseReason** - WebSocket close reason, e.g. Abnormal close, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8319">**DataIsFreshCount** – sėkmingų užklausų iš „Web Socket“ seanso skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8319">**DataIsFreshCount** - number of successful pull requests in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8320">**DeviceSessionId** – įrenginio seanso ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8320">**DeviceSessionId** - Device session ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8321">**DownloadCount** – Atsisiuntimų skaičius „Web Socket“ seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8321">**DownloadCount** - number of downloads in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8322">**Error** – yra iš esmės Exception_Type + Exception_Description + Exception_Code + Exception_Tag</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8322">**Error** - is basically Exception_Type + Exception_Description + Exception_Code + Exception_Tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8323">**Exception_Code** – skaitinis arba raidinis kodas, naudojamas nustatyti klaidos pobūdį ir (arba), kodėl ji įvyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8323">**Exception_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of an error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8324">**Exception_Description** – trumpas klaidos aprašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8324">**Exception_Description** - a description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8325">**Exception_Tag** – nurodo vietą kode, kur yra klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8325">**Exception_Tag** - indicate where in the code throws the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8326">**Exception_Type** – klaidos tipas, pvz. Win32Error ir t.t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8326">**Exception_Type** - the type of the error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8327">**FirstUpdateSize** – pirmo atnaujinimo pranešimo ilgis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8327">**FirstUpdateSize** - first update message length</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8328">**HasError** – ar įvyko klaida „Web Socket“ seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8328">**HasError** - whether there is an error during the WebSocket session</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8329">**IsEducationNotebook** – ar dabartinis bloknotas yra išsilavinimo bloknotas, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8329">**IsEducationNotebook** - Is the current notebook education notebook or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8330">**IsHierarchyResource** – ar dabartiniai ištekliai yra puslapyje, ar sekcijoje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8330">**IsHierarchyResource** - Is the current resource a page or a section</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8331">**NotebookId** – „OneNote“ bloknoto ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8331">**NotebookId** - OneNote notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8332">**OperationWithError** – kurios operacijos metu įvyko klaida, pvz., WebSocket.Close, WebSocket.Open ir t.t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8332">**OperationWithError** - in which operation did the error happen, e.g. WebSocket.Close, WebSocket.Open, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8333">**ResourceId** – „OneNote“ puslapio arba skyriaus išteklių ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8333">**ResourceId** - OneNote page or section resource ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8334">**SectionId** – „OneNote“ skyriaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8334">**SectionId** - OneNote section ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8335">**ServerSessionId** – seanso ID, naudojamas susieti „WebSocket“ prašymą su onenote.com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8335">**ServerSessionId** - session ID used to correlate WebSocket request to onenote.com</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8336">**SessionDurationInMs** – „WebSocket“ seanso trukmė milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8336">**SessionDurationInMs** - the duration in milliseconds of the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8337">**TenantId** – „SharePoint“ nuomotojo ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8337">**TenantId** - SharePoint tenant ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8338">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** laikas milisekundėmis gaunant pirmąjį atnaujinimą iš serverio, kai vyksta „WebSocket“ seansas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8338">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** - time in milliseconds taken to receive first update from the server side after the WebSocket session is established</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8339">**UploadAckCount** – nusiuntimo skaičius „WebSocket“ seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8339">**UploadAckCount** - number of acknowledges for upload in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8340">**WebUrl** -PII ir trinamas žiniatinklio URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8340">**WebUrl** - PII scrubbed web URL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8380">**Error_Code** – skaitinis arba raidinis kodas, naudojamas nustatyti klaidos pobūdį ir (arba), kodėl ji įvyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8380">**Error_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of an error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8381">**Error_Description** – trumpas klaidos aprašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8381">**Error_Description** - a description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8382">**Error_Tag** – nurodo, kur kode įvyksta klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8382">**Error_Tag** - indicate where in the code throws the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8383">**Error_Type** – klaidos tipas, pvz., „Win32Error“ ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8383">**Error_Type** - the type of the error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8384">**ErrorText** – vartotojo sąsajos rodomas klaidos tekstas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8384">**ErrorText** - error text shown in the UI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8385">**Explanation** – paaiškinama, kokius laukiančius siuntimo pakeitimus reikia perkelti į netinkamoje vietoje esančius skyrius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8385">**Explanation** - explains what kind of pending outbound changes that need to be moved to misplaced sections</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8386">**fishbowlType** – „Fishbowl“ tipas pvz., Page Fishbowl, Section Fishbowl ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8386">**fishbowlType** - type of fishbowl, e.g. page fishbowl, section fishbowl, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8387">**IDS** – vartotojo sąsajos rodomo teksto sveikasis identifikavimo ženklas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8387">**IDS** - an integer identifier for the text shown in the UI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8389">**IsUsingRealtimeHierarchySync** – ar naudoja modernų hierarchinį sinchronizavimą, ar ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8389">**IsUsingRealtimeHierarchySync** - Is using modern hierarchy sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8390">**NotebookId** – bloknoto ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8390">**NotebookId** - notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8391">**PageSyncUIState** – puslapių sinchronizavimo būsenos eilutė, pvz., UpToDate, Syncing, SaveOffline, SyncError ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8391">**PageSyncUIState** - page sync status string, e.g., UpToDate, Syncing, SaveOffline, SyncError, etc.</span></span>

### <a name="onenoteappprovisioningmovelocalnotebooktoonlinenotebookfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8394">OneNote.App.Provisioning.MoveLocalNotebookToOnlineNotebookFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8394">OneNote.App.Provisioning.MoveLocalNotebookToOnlineNotebookFailed</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8395">Šis įvykis užregistruojamas, kai nepavyksta perkelti vietinio bloknoto į diską.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8395">This event is logged when move of local notebook to drive fails.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8396">Šis scenarijus būdingas atidėtam vartotojo prisijungimui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8396">This scenario is specific to delayed sign-in user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8397">Kai vartotojas prisijungia, vietinis bloknotas persiunčiamas į jo „OneDrive“ saugyklą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8397">When the user signs in, their local notebook is transferred to their OneDrive storage.</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8398">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8398">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8399">**ErrorMsg** – klaidos pranešimas, atitinkantis triktį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8399">**ErrorMsg** - The error message corresponding to the failure.</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestorageconnectivitychanged"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8400">OneNote.Storage.ConnectivityChanged</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8400">OneNote.Storage.ConnectivityChanged</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8401">Įvykis registruoja, ar vartotojas turi interneto ryšį, ar ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8401">The event logs if a user has internet connectivity or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8402">Tai naudojama norint susieti kitas sinchronizavimo sveikatos charakteristikos metrikas, leidžiant mums nepaisyti įvykių, kurie įvyksta, kai vartotojas neturi interneto ryšio, nes nesitikime, kad mūsų paslaugos gaištis yra priimtina be interneto ryšio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8402">This is used to correlate the other sync health performance metrics by allowing us to ignore events that occur while a user does not have internet connectivity as we do not expect our service latency to be acceptable without internet connectivity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8403">Tai leidžia mums apskaičiuoti tikslų seansų skaičių mūsų metrikai klientams (kiekvienam nuomotojui, kiekvienam sektoriui).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8403">This allows us to calculate an accurate session count for our metrics across slices of customers (per-tenant, per-sector).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8404">Tai taip pat naudojama filtruoti klaidų ataskaitas, nes yra daug sinchronizavimo klaidų, kurios, tikėtina, įvyktų be tinklo ryšio, bet tai pateisina tyrimą kitu atveju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8404">We also use it to filter error reports as there are numerous sync errors that we expect to occur without network connectivity but that warrant investigation otherwise.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8405">Negavę šių duomenų negalėsime tiksliai stebėti mūsų produktų produktyvumo arba nustatyti, ar tikėtina, kad vartotojas patiria klaidų, ar reikės atlikti tolesnį tyrimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8405">If we do not receive this data, we will not be able to accurately monitor our products performance or determine if errors experienced by a user are expected or require further investigation.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8406">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8406">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8407">**"InternetConnectivityNowAvailable"** – jei ryšio būsena buvo pakeista, kad dabar būtų internete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8407">**InternetConnectivityNowAvailable** -  If the connectivity state has been changed so it is now Internet</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragelegacyinboundlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8408">OneNote.Storage.LegacyInboundLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8408">OneNote.Storage.LegacyInboundLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8409">Kritiniu signalu, kuris naudojamas gaunamoms sinchronizavimo operacijoms, kurios tiesiogiai bendrauja su „SharePoint“, įskaitant koreliacijos informaciją, kad galėtume stebėti ir tirti duomenų įkėlimo į mūsų tarnybą rezultatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8409">The critical signal used to track the performance of inbound sync operations that communicate directly with SharePoint including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of uploading data to our service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8410">Šis signalas renkamas tik blogiausiam atsisiuntimo našumui per paskutines 300 sekundžių („Microsoft“ konfigūruojamas sekundžių skaičius priklausomai nuo paslaugos produktyvumo ir būklės).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8410">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8411">Tai naudojama siekiant užtikrinti tarnybos sveikatą, leidžiant mums matyti, kurie nuomotojai patiria nepriimtinai lėtą duomenų gavimą į mūsų tarnybą, informaciją apie duomenis, kuriuos jie įkelia, kai patiria lėtą informacijos gavimą, ir kaip plačiai ši gaišties problema paplitusi nuomotojuje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8411">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow inbound of data to our service, information about the data they are uploading when they experienced the slow inbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8412">Be to, tai naudojama pranešti apie tarnybų sveikatą ir veikimo rezultatus mūsų klientams, kad būtų galima išmatuoti tendencijas per tam tikrą laiką ir automatiškai spręsti problemas, susijusias su gamybos mažinimu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8412">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8413">Neturėdami šių duomenų, negalėsime užtikrinti tinkamo atsisiuntimo vykdymo, kai vartotojas sinchronizuoja pakeitimus iš „SharePoint“ į savo kompiuterį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8413">If we do not have this data it will prevent us from ensuring adequate download performance when a user syncs changes from SharePoint to their computer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8414">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8414">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8415">**Iseducationnotebook** - Bulio logika nurodanti, ar bloknotas yra švietimo įstaigos bloknotas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8415">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8416">**NotebookId** - šio nusiuntimo bloknoto ID </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8416">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8417">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - laikas milisekundėmis, kurį truko įkėlimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8417">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragelegacyoutboundlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8418">OneNote.Storage.LegacyOutboundLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8418">OneNote.Storage.LegacyOutboundLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8419">Kritinis signalas, kuris naudojamas gaunamoms sinchronizavimo operacijoms, kurios tiesiogiai bendrauja su „SharePoint“, įskaitant koreliacijos informaciją, kad galėtume stebėti ir tirti duomenų įkėlimo į mūsų tarnybą rezultatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8419">The critical signal used to track the performance of outbound sync operations that communicate directly with SharePoint including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of uploading data to our service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8420">Šis signalas renkamas tik blogiausiam atsisiuntimo našumui per paskutines 300 sekundžių („Microsoft“ konfigūruojamas sekundžių skaičius priklausomai nuo paslaugos produktyvumo ir būklės).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8420">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8421">Tai naudojama siekiant užtikrinti tarnybos sveikatą, leidžiant mums matyti, kurie nuomotojai patiria nepriimtinai lėtą duomenų siuntimą iš mūsų tarnybos, informaciją apie duomenis, kuriuos jie įkelia, kai patiria lėtą informacijos gavimą, ir kaip plačiai ši gaišties problema paplitusi nuomotojuje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8421">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow outbound of data to our service, information about the data they were uploading when they experienced the slow outbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8422">Be to, tai naudojama pranešti apie tarnybų sveikatą ir veikimo rezultatus mūsų klientams, kad būtų galima išmatuoti tendencijas per tam tikrą laiką ir automatiškai pranešti apie problemas, susijusias su gamybos mažinimu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8422">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8423">Neturėdami šių duomenų, negalėsime užtikrinti tinkamo veikimo, kai vartotojas sinchronizuoja pakeitimus iš „SharePoint“ į savo kompiuterį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8423">If we do not have this data, it will prevent us from ensuring adequate performance when syncing users changes up to SharePoint.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8424">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8424">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8425">**Iseducationnotebook** - Bulio logika nurodanti, ar bloknotas yra švietimo įstaigos bloknotas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8425">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8426">**NotebookId** - šio nusiuntimo bloknoto ID </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8426">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8427">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - laikas milisekundėmis, kurį truko įkėlimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8427">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds it took to perform the upload</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimefiledataobjectdownload"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8428">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.FileDataObjectDownload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8428">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.FileDataObjectDownload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8429">Kritinis signalas, naudojamas veikimui sekti, kai vartotojas gauna duomenų objekto failą (t. y. įdėtasis failas arba atvaizdas), atsisiųstą tiesiai iš mūsų tarnybos, o ne kaip sinchronizavimo operacijos dalį puslapyje, sekcijoje ar bloknote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8429">The critical signal used to track performance when a user inbounds a file data object (i.e. an embedded file or image) which is downloaded directly from our service and not as part of a sync operation on a page, section or notebook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8430">Šis signalas renkamas tik blogiausiam atsisiuntimo našumui per paskutines 300 sekundžių („Microsoft“ konfigūruojamas sekundžių skaičius priklausomai nuo paslaugos produktyvumo ir būklės).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8430">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8431">Tai naudojama siekiant užtikrinti tarnybos sveikatą ir veikimą, nes mes galime matyti, kurie nuomotojai patiria nepageidautinai lėtą duomenų atsisiuntimą iš mūsų tarnybos, ir apie tai, kaip plačiai paplitusi nuomotojuje gaišties problema, bei pranešti apie savo elgseną per tam tikrą laiką, kad galėtume išmatuoti tarnybos našumo tendencijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8431">This is used to ensure service health and performance by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow download of data from our service, and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is, and report our behavior over time allowing us to measure service performance trends.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8432">Pastebėję nepriimtiną failo objekto gaištį, taip pat naudosime šiuos duomenis susieti tai su kitais signalais apie šį objektą iš kliento ir tarnybos, kad patobulintume savo atsiuntimo procesą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8432">If we see an unacceptable latency for a file object, we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the object to make improvements to our download process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8433">Taip pat išskaidome duomenis atsižvelgdami į failų objekto plėtinį, kuris buvo atsisiųstas, atsižvelgiant į tai, ar šis failas yra įdėtasis mūsų drobėje (pvz., vaizde), ar tai nėra įdėtasis failas (pvz., tekstinis dokumentas).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8433">We also split the data based on the extension of the file object downloaded as we have different expectations based on whether the file is presented inline in our canvas (e.g. an image) or is a non-inline file (such as a text document).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8434">Negavę šių duomenų negalėsime stebėti šių atsisiuntimų veiklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8434">If we do not receive this data, it will prevent us from monitoring the performance of these downloads</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8435">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8435">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8436">**FileSizeInBytes** – atsisiunčiamo failo dydis baitais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8436">**FileSizeInBytes** - The size of the file being downloaded in bytes</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8437">**Isimage** - Bulio logika nustatyti, ar atsisiųstą failą sudaro plėtinys, kuris atitinka iš dalies nustatytą įprastų vaizdo formatų sąrašą (.bmp, .emf, .gif, .jpe, .jpeg, .jpg, .png), kuriame rodomas įdėtasis drobės vaizdas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8437">**IsImage** - A bool determining if the file being downloaded has an extension that matches a pre-determined list of common image formats (.bmp, .emf, .gif, .jpe, .jpeg, .jpg, .png) that we display inline in the canvas</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8438">**TimeToDownload** – kiek laiko užtrunka sėkmingai atsisiųsti FDO iš mūsų blob saugyklos į įrenginį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8438">**TimeToDownload** - The length of time it took to successfully download the FDO from our blob storage to the device</span></span> 

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimewebsocketdownload"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8439">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketDownload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8439">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketDownload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8440">Kritinis signalas, kuris naudojamas gaunamoms sinchronizavimo operacijoms, kurios tiesiogiai bendrauja su „SharePoint“, įskaitant koreliacijos informaciją, kad galėtume stebėti ir tirti duomenų atsiuntimo iš mūsų tarnybos (onenote.com) rezultatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8440">The critical signal used to track performance of inbound sync operations including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of downloading data from our service (onenote.com).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8441">Šis signalas renkamas tik blogiausiam atsisiuntimo našumui per paskutines 300 sekundžių („Microsoft“ konfigūruojamas sekundžių skaičius priklausomai nuo paslaugos produktyvumo ir būklės).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8441">This signal is only collected for the worst performing download in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8442">Tai naudojama siekiant užtikrinti tarnybos sveikatą, leidžiant mums matyti, kurie nuomotojai patiria nepriimtinai lėtą duomenų gavimą iš mūsų tarnybos, informaciją apie duomenis, kuriuos siuntė, kai patyrė lėtą informacijos gavimą, ir kaip plačiai ši gaišties problema paplitusi nuomotojuje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8442">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see which tenants are experiencing an unacceptably slow inbound of data from our service, information about the data they were downloading when they experienced the slow inbound and how widespread within a tenant that latency issue is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8443">Be to, tai naudojama pranešti apie tarnybų sveikatą ir veikimo rezultatus mūsų klientams, kad būtų galima išmatuoti tendencijas per tam tikrą laiką ir automatiškai pranešti apie problemas, susijusias su gamybos mažinimu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8443">It is also used to report service health and performance across our customers to measure trends over time and alert on issues automatically for engineering mitigation.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8444">Jei pastebėsime netinkamą sekcijos ar bloknoto gaištį, taip pat naudosime šiuos duomenis susieti ją su kitais signalais iš kliento ar tarnybos apie tą patį dokumentą, kad identifikuotume našumo regresiją ir galėtume teikti geresnę patirtį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8444">If we see an unacceptable latency for a section or notebook we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the same document to identify client-side performance regressions allowing us to deliver a more performant service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8445">Negavę šių duomenų negalėsime stebėti mūsų tarnybos šio aspekto našumo arba serverio keitimų poveikio, kurie gali būti reikalingi dėl naudojimo ar kitų faktorių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8445">If we do not receive this data, we will be unable to monitor the performance of this aspect of our service, or the impact of server side changes we may find necessary due to usage or other factors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8446">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8446">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8447">**DeviceSessionId** - Įrenginio sesijos ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8447">**DeviceSessionId** -  The ID of the device session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8448">**Iseducationnotebook** - Bulio logika nurodanti, ar bloknotas yra švietimo įstaigos bloknotas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8448">**IsEducationNotebook** - A bool indicating if the notebook is an education notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8449">**IsHierarchyResource** - Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar šaltinis yra hierarchijos šaltinis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8449">**IsHierarchyResource** - A bool indicating if the resource is a hierarchy resource</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8450">**NotebookId** - šio nusiuntimo bloknoto ID </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8450">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8451">**ResourceId** - nusiunčiamo ištekliaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8451">**ResourceId** - The ID of the resource that we are uploading</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8452">**SectionId** - šio nusiuntimo sekcijos ID </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8452">**SectionId** - The ID of the section that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8453">**ServerSessionId** - šio nusiuntimo serverio sesijos ID </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8453">**ServerSessionId** - The ID of the server session that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8454">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - laikas milisekundėmis tarp vartotojo perėjimo į puslapį ir replikavimo rietuvės, kuri patvirtina, kad puslapis sinchronizuojamas su serveriu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8454">**TimeToConfirmSyncedWithServerInMs** - The time in milliseconds between a user navigating to a page and the replication stack confirming that page is in sync with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8455">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** - laikas milisekundėmis tarp sinchronizavimo modulio, kuris pradeda gavimo repliką ir replikavimo operaciją, pasiekiamą sinchronizuojant su serverio būsena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8455">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** - The time in milliseconds between the sync engine beginning inbound replication of a page and that replication operation reaching the in sync with the server state.</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragerealtimewebsocketupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8456">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8456">OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8457">Kritinis signalas, kuris naudojamas siunčiamoms sinchronizavimo operacijoms, kurios tiesiogiai bendrauja su „SharePoint“, įskaitant koreliacijos informaciją, kad galėtume stebėti ir tirti duomenų nusiuntimo į mūsų tarnybas (onenote.com) rezultatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8457">The critical signal used to track the performance of outbound sync operations including correlating information allowing us to monitor and investigate the performance of uploading data to our service (onenote.com)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8461">Jei pastebėsime netinkamą sekcijos ar bloknoto gaištį, taip pat naudosime šiuos duomenis susieti ją su kitais signalais iš kliento ar tarnybos apie tą patį dokumentą, kad identifikuotume našumo regresiją ir galėtume teikti geresnę patirtį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8461">If we see an unacceptable latency for a section or notebook we will also use this data to correlate that with other signals from the client and service regarding the same document to identify performance regressions allowing us to deliver a more performant experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8462">Negavę šių duomenų negalėsime stebėti mūsų tarnybos šio aspekto našumo arba serverio keitimų poveikio, kurie gali būti reikalingi dėl naudojimo ar kitų faktorių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8462">If we do not receive this data, we will be unable to monitor the performance of this aspect of our service, or the impact of server side changes we may find necessary due to usage or other factors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8463">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8463">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8467">**IsWorstTime** - Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar laikas yra reguliarus nusiuntimo įvykis, ar blogiausias mūsų matytas laikas šiame kliente per paskutines 300 sekundžių (sekundžių skaičius gali būti konfigūruojamas „Microsoft“ priklausomai nuo tarnybos našumo ir būsenos).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8467">**IsWorstTime** - A bool indicating if the time is a regular upload event, or the worst time we saw on this client in the last 300 seconds (the number of seconds is configurable by Microsoft depending on service performance and condition).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8468">**NotebookId** - šio nusiuntimo bloknoto ID </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8468">**NotebookId** - The ID of the notebook that this upload is part of</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8469">**RecommendedPutIntervalInMs** - laikas, kurį tarnyba praneš klientui, kaip jos rekomenduotą intervalą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8469">**RecommendedPutIntervalInMs** - The time the service has communicated to the client as its recommended put interval</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8470">**ResourceId** - nusiunčiamo ištekliaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8470">**ResourceId** - The ID of the resource that we are uploading</span></span>

### <a name="onenotestoragesynchealth"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8478">OneNote.Storage.SyncHealth</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8478">OneNote.Storage.SyncHealth</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8479">Kritinis signalas, kuris naudojamas sekti klaidas ir išimtis, kurios įvyko sinchronizavimo rietuvėje „OneNote“ kliente, leidžiantis mums stebėti ir sušvelninti šias nenumatytas sąlygas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8479">The critical signal used to track errors and exceptions that have occurred inside the sync stack in the OneNote client allowing us to monitor and mitigate these unexpected conditions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8480">Tai naudojama užtikrinant tarnybos sveikatą, nes leidžia mums matyti klientų klaidų ataskaitas beveik realiuoju laiku, o tai leidžia mums atsakyti į sinchronizavimo problemas, kai jos iškyla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8480">This is used to ensure service health by allowing us to see error reports from the clients in near real time, which lets us respond to sync issues as they arise.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8481">Tai taip pat naudojama norint nustatyti, kaip plačiai paplitusi problema, ir kaip smarkiai skiriasi, kai klaidos žymė yra susieta su kliento kodu, kad būtų identifikuojamas gedimo šaltinis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8481">It is also used to identify how widespread an issue is, and how severe by cross-referencing the error tag with the client code to identify the source of failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8482">Mes taip pat pateikiame šiuos duomenis, kad gautumėte informacijos apie mūsų našumą bei mūsų klientų ir tarnybų patobulinimų įtaką ir efektyvumą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8482">We also aggregate this data to get information on our performance over time and the impact and effectiveness of improvements we make to our clients and services.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8483">Jei neturime šių duomenų, mes negalime aktyviai reaguoti į klaidas, esančias mūsų sinchronizavimo tarnyboje be klientų eskalavimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8483">If we do not have this data, we won’t be able to proactively respond to error conditions in our sync service without customer escalation.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8484">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8484">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8485">**Service** – Sinchronizavimo tarnyba, kurią naudojo klientas, kai įvyko klaida (pasenusi versija arba šiuolaikinis sinchronizavimas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8485">**Service** - The sync service the client was using when the error occurred (Legacy or Modern Sync)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8486">**Tag** – žymė (identifikuojanti reikšmė), vaizduojanti klaidą, su kurią klientas susidūrė sinchronizavimo operacijos metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8486">**Tag** - The tag (an identifying value) representing the error that the client encountered during the sync operation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8488">Šis įvykis užregistruojamas, kai nepavyksta sukurti bloknoto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8488">This event is logged when creation of a notebook fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8490">**NetworkConnection** – užregistruojamas ryšio, kuriuo šiuo metu prijungtas įrenginys, tipas, pvz., „Wi-Fi“, neprijungtas, 3G</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8490">**NetworkConnection** - Logs the connection type that the device is currently on e.g. Wi-Fi, offline, 3G</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8493">Šis įvykis užregistruojamas, kai įvyksta trumpųjų pastabų sinchronizavimo triktis vartotojui pirmą kartą naudojantis paslauga įrenginyje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8493">This event is logged when syncing of Quick Notes failed for a user during their First Run Experience on a device.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8494">Tai būdinga pirmojo paslaugos naudojimo scenarijui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8494">This is specific to the First Run scenario.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8495">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8495">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8496">**NetworkConnection** – užregistruojamas ryšio, kuriuo šiuo metu prijungtas įrenginys, tipas, pvz., „Wi-Fi“, neprijungtas, 3G</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8496">**NetworkConnection** - Logs the connection type that the device is currently on e.g. Wi-Fi, offline, 3G</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8497">**ServerType** – užregistruojamas serverio, kuriame turėjo būti sukurtas trumpųjų pastabų bloknotas, tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8497">**ServerType** - Logs the server type where Quick Notes notebook was to be created</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8502">Šis įvykis padeda stebėti kalendoriaus susitikimo paleidimo naudojimą įvairiuose galiniuose punktuose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8502">This event helps to track the usage of calendar meeting launch, across different endpoints.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8503">Šis įvykis leidžia mums nustatyti du dalykus, kai susitikimas paleidžiamas naudojant „Skype“ verslui, kai susitikimas paleidžiamas per „Teams“ ir jei įdiegta „Teams“ programa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8503">This event lets us detect two things when a meeting is launched via Skype for Business, and when a meeting is launched via Teams, and if the Teams app is installed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8504">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8504">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8505">**account** – Maišos paskyros informacija, kuri atliko veiksmą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8505">**account** - Hashed account information which performed the action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8506">**action_type** – atliktas veiksmas, pvz., susitikimo paleidimas ar programos diegimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8506">**action_type** - action performed, such as launch meeting or install application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8507">**application** – programa, kuri buvo paleista naudojant gilųjį saitą, pvz., „Teams“ ar „Skype“ verslui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8507">**application** - Application that was launched via a deep link, such as Teams or Skype for Business</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8538">**failureReason** – eilutė – įtraukiama, kai būsena yra „triktis“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8538">**failureReason** - String – Only added when status is “failure”.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8539">Nurodomas klaidos atsakas, pateikiamas RFS parengimo atsako.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8539">Indicating the error response given by the RFS Provisioning response.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8540">**productId** – eilutė – produkto „App Store“ ID, kuriam buvo pateikta užklausa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8540">**productId** - String – App Store ID of the product the request was made for</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8541">**status** – eilutė – sėkmė arba triktis, nurodanti, ar užklausa pavyko, ar nepavyko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8541">**status** - String – Success or Failure, indicating if the request succeeded or failed</span></span>


### <a name="officeiospaywallstorekitresponse"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8542">Office.iOS.Paywall.StoreKit.Response</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8542">Office.iOS.Paywall.StoreKit.Response</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8543">Duomenys renkami kaip kritinė inžinerinė telemetrija, skirta registruoti pirkimo bandymo rezultatą, kurį neautomatiškai inicijavo vartotojas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8543">The data is collected as critical engineering telemetry to log the result of purchase attempt triggered manually by user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8544">Produkto telemetrija naudojama norint suderinti pirkimo operacijos informaciją su „Microsoft“ komercijos sistema, kad būtų galima įgalinti susietas prenumeratos privilegijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8544">The product telemetry is used for reconciliation of purchase transaction information with the Microsoft commerce system to enable associated subscription benefits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8545">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8545">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8546">**entryPoint** – eilutė – mygtukas arba srautas iš kurio buvo rodoma mokama prieiga prie informacijos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8546">**entryPoint** - String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8547">Pvz., „Premium Upgrade Button“ („Premium“ atnaujinimo mygtukas“) arba „First Run Flow“ (pirmojo vykdymo srautas).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8547">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8548">**failureReason** – eilutė – įtraukiama, kai būsena yra „triktis“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8548">**failureReason** - String – Only added when status is “failure”.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8549">Nurodomas klaidos atsakas, pateikiamas „App Store“ atsako.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8549">Indicating the error response given by the App-store response</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8550">**productId** – eilutė – tik „MakePurchase“, „PendingPurchase“, „App Store“ produkto ID, kuriam užklausa buvo sukurta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8550">**productId** - String – Only for “MakePurchase”, “PendingPurchase”, the app-store ID of the product for which the request was made.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8551">**productsCount** – sveikasis skaičius – tik „ProductsFetch“, produktų skaičius, grąžintas „Store“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8551">**productsCount** - Int – Only for “ProductsFetch”, the number of products returned by Store.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemgracefulexitgracefulappexitdesktop"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8582">Office.System.GracefulExit.GracefulAppExitDesktop</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8582">Office.System.GracefulExit.GracefulAppExitDesktop</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8583">Įvykį sukelia sklandus „Office“ klientų programų, tokių kaip, tačiau neapsiribojant „Word“, „Excel“, „PowerPoint“ ir „Outlook“, nutraukimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8583">The event is triggered by a graceful application termination for Office client applications such as, but not limited to, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8584">„Office“ klientų produktų būklei įvertinti naudojame sklandų išėjimą iš programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8584">We use Graceful Exit to measure the health of Office client products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8585">Tai yra verslui svarbus signalas, kurį naudoja „Office“ inžinieriai, siekdami užtikrinti produkto stabilumą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8585">It is intended to be a business-critical signal used by Office engineers to infer product stability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8586">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8586">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8587">**AppBuild** – paveikto proceso komponavimo versijos identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8587">**AppBuild** - Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8588">**AppMajor** – paveikto proceso pagrindinės versijos identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8588">**AppMajor** - Major version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8589">**AppMinor** – paveikto proceso papildomos versijos identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8589">**AppMinor** - Minor version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8590">**AppRevision** – paveikto proceso komponavimo versijos identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8590">**AppRevision** - Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8591">**BootCompleted** – ar „Office“ procesas baigė įkrovą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8591">**BootCompleted** – Did Office process complete boot.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8592">**DetectionTime** – netikėto išėjimo aptikimo laikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8592">**DetectionTime** - The time when the unexpected exit was detected.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8593">**ecsETag** – proceso eksperimento identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8593">**EcsETag** - An experiment identifier for the process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8594">**HasEdit** – ar „Office“ proceso metu buvo atliekamas dokumento redagavimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8594">**HasEdit** – Was document editing occurring during the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8595">**HasOpen** – ar „Office“ proceso metu buvo atidaromas dokumentas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8595">**HasOpen** – Was document opened during the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8596">**InstallMethod** – ar į dabartinę „Office“ komponavimo versiją buvo atnaujinta, ji buvo įdiegta atšaukus keitimus, ar tai nauja įdiegtis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8596">**InstallMethod** - Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from, rolled back to, or a fresh install.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8597">**OfficeUILang** – „Office“ proceso kalba.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8597">**OfficeUILang** – Language of the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8598">**PreviousBuild** – anksčiau įdiegta komponavimo versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8598">**PreviousBuild** - Previously installed build version.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8599">**SafeMode** – ar „Office“ procesas buvo vykdomas saugiuoju režimu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8599">**SafeMode** – Was Office process in safe mode.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8600">**SessionId** – proceso unikalusis identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8600">**SessionId** - A unique identifier of the process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8601">**SessionInitTime** – paveikto proceso pradžios laikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8601">**SessionInitTime** - The time when the affected process started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8991">**AffectedProcessExeMinorVersion –** paveikto proceso papildomos versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8991">**AffectedProcessExeMinorVersion -** The Minor Version number of the affected process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-8992">*[Šis laukas buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-8992">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemsystemhealthungracefulappexitimmersive"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9071">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulAppExitImmersive</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9071">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulAppExitImmersive</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9072">Naudojama gaunant gedimo metriką.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9072">Used to capture crash metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9073">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9073">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemsystemhealthungracefulapplicationexitwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9100">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulApplicationExitWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9100">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulApplicationExitWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9101">Įvykį sukelia neįprastas programos nutraukimas (pvz., užduočių tvarkyklės uždarymas, programos pakibimas ir kt.), jis skirtas „Office“ kliento programoms, tokioms kaip, bet tuo neapsiribojant, „Word“, „Excel“, „PowerPoint“ ir „Outlook“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9101">The event is triggers by an abnormal application termination (for example, task manager kill, application hang, etc.) for Office client applications such as, but not limited to, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9102">„Office“ klientų produktų būklei įvertinti naudojame nesklandaus išėjimo iš programos metriką.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9102">We use Ungraceful Application Exit metrics to measure the health of Office client products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9103">Tai yra verslui svarbus signalas, kurį naudoja „Office“ inžinieriai, siekdami užtikrinti produkto stabilumą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9103">It is a business-critical signal used by Office engineers to infer product stability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9104">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9104">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9105">**AddinExecution –** vėliavėlė, kuri nurodo, ar papildinys buvo vykdomas ir nepabaigtas nesklandaus išėjimo iš programos metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9105">**AddinExecution** - Flag that informs if an add-in was executing and didn't finish during an ungraceful application exit.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9106">*[Šis laukas buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9106">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9107">**AppUsedVirtualMemory** - virtuali atmintis naudojama „Office“ programoje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9107">**AppUsedVirtualMemory** - Virtual memory utilized by office application</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9108">**BootCompleted –** ar buvo užbaigtas „Office“ paleidimas gedimo metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9108">**BootCompleted** - Was Office boot completed at the time of crash.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9109">*[Šis laukas buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9109">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9110">**BucketId** - gedimo „Watson“ skirstymo identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9110">**BucketId** - Watson bucket Identifier for crash</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9111">**CabGuid** - globaliai unikalus identifikatorius (GUID) skirtas „Watson“ cab failui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9111">**CabGuid** - Globally Unique Identifier (GUID) identifier for the Watson cab.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9112">**CrashedAppBuild** - paveikto proceso komponavimo versijos identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9112">**CrashedAppBuild** - Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9113">*[Šis laukas buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9113">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9114">**CrashedAppMajor** - paveikto proceso pagrindinės versijos identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9114">**CrashedAppMajor** - Major version identifier for the affected process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9115">*[Šis laukas buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9115">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9116">**CrashedAppMinor** - paveikto proceso papildomos versijos identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9116">**CrashedAppMinor** - Minor version identifier for the affected process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9117">*[Šis laukas buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9117">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9118">**CrashedAppVersion** - proceso, kuriame įvyko gedimas, programos versijos identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9118">**CrashedAppVersion** - Application version identifier for crashed process.</span></span>
