  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9120">**CrashedModuleName** - modulio su klaida pavadinimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9120">**CrashedModuleName** - Failing module name.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9121">**CrashedProcessSessionId** - proceso, kuriame įvyko gedimas, unikalusis identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9121">**CrashedProcessSessionId** - A unique identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9122">**CrashedProcessSessionInitTime** - paveikto proceso pradžios laikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9122">**CrashedProcessSessionInitTime** - The time when the affected process started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9123">**CrashedSessionInitTime –** paveikto proceso pabaigos laikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9123">**CrashedProcessSessionUninitTime** - The time when the affected process ended.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9124">**CrashTag** – unikalus gedimo kodo identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9124">**CrashTag** - The unique identifier for the code of the crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9125">**CrashTime –** laikas, nurodantis, kada klientas netikėtai nutraukė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9125">**CrashTime** - The time indicating the client terminated ungracefully.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9126">*[Šis laukas buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9126">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9128">**DetectionTime** – netikėto išėjimo aptikimo laikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9128">**DetectionTime** - The time when the unexpected exit was detected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9129">*[Šis laukas buvo pašalintas iš dabartinių „Office“ versijų, bet gali būti rodomas senesnėse versijose.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9129">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9132">**ExceptionCode** - išimties skirstymo identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9132">**ExceptionCode** - Bucketing identifier for the exception.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9209">**PreviousBuild –** anksčiau įdiegta komponavimo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9209">**PreviousBuild -** Previously installed build version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9210">**PreviousInteractionSessionTime –** ankstesnio sąveikos seanso pradžios laikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9210">**PreviousInteractionSessionTime -** Time which the previous interaction session started.</span></span>

### <a name="officetelemetryvolumetrackingdata"></a><span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9495">Office.Telemetry.VolumeTrackingData</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9495">Office.Telemetry.VolumeTrackingData</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9496">Telemetrjos įvykių kiekio stebėjimo metrika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9496">Event volume tracking metrics for telemetry events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9497">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9497">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9498">**EventThreshold** – didžiausias vieno įvykio egzempliorių, kuriuos galima išsiųsti laikotarpiu, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9498">**EventThreshold** - The maximum number of instances of a single event that can be sent in a window of time.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9499">**HighestEventCount** – didžiausias vieno įvykio egzempliorių, išsiųstų šiuo laikotarpiu, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9499">**HighestEventCount** - The highest number of instances of a single event sent this window.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="41ba8-9500">**HighestEventName** – įvykio, kurio egzempliorių skaičius šiuo laikotarpiu didžiausias, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="41ba8-9500">**HighestEventName** - The name of the event with the highest number of instances in this window.</span></span>
